##
Kind: captions

00:00:20.309 --> 00:00:25.914 position:16% line:89% align:start
[kids laughing, talking]

00:00:38.060 --> 00:00:39.661 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>In this world,</i>

00:00:39.695 --> 00:00:41.063 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>there's an</i>
 <i>invisible magic circle.</i>

00:00:42.731 --> 00:00:45.801 position:13% line:89% align:start
[kids talking, overlapping]

00:00:45.834 --> 00:00:47.169 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:00:47.202 --> 00:00:49.972 position:5% line:83% align:start
- So you were really dating him?
- Tell us more!

00:00:52.941 --> 00:00:56.678 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>There's an inside</i>
 <i>and an outside.</i>

00:00:56.712 --> 00:00:58.348 position:13% line:83% align:start
- I can't draw this at all.
- Me neither.

00:00:58.381 --> 00:00:59.915 position:16% line:89% align:start
Well, what's the problem?

00:00:59.948 --> 00:01:01.284 position:35% line:89% align:start
Let me see.

00:01:01.317 --> 00:01:04.586 position:19% line:83% align:start
What? No. I'll show you
when I'm done. Please.

00:01:04.620 --> 00:01:06.622 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Those people are</i>
 <i>inside the circle.</i>

00:01:10.059 --> 00:01:11.960 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>And I'm outside.</i>

00:01:13.229 --> 00:01:15.165 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>But it doesn't really matter.</i>

00:01:17.067 --> 00:01:18.101 position:30% line:89% align:start
How's it going?

00:01:18.901 --> 00:01:19.902 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:01:22.005 --> 00:01:24.941 position:5% line:89% align:start
Oh... no... I kind of messed up.

00:01:24.974 --> 00:01:26.276 position:24% line:89% align:start
Let me have a look.

00:01:26.309 --> 00:01:27.310 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uh...

00:01:36.052 --> 00:01:39.089 position:35% line:83% align:start
[thudding]
[kid crying]

00:01:39.122 --> 00:01:41.091 position:21% line:89% align:start
Oh, no. Are you okay?

00:01:41.124 --> 00:01:42.591 position:21% line:89% align:start
Oh, what's going on?

00:01:44.427 --> 00:01:45.829 position:30% line:83% align:start
[man, distant]
What happened?

00:01:46.930 --> 00:01:49.065 position:10% line:89% align:start
[playground sounds fade away]

00:01:49.099 --> 00:01:50.100 position:38% line:89% align:start
[coughs]

00:01:52.135 --> 00:01:53.269 position:44% line:89% align:start
 <i>I...</i>

00:01:54.804 --> 00:01:56.372 position:27% line:89% align:start
[wood splinters]

00:01:56.406 --> 00:01:58.007 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>I hate myself.</i>

00:01:58.041 --> 00:02:01.111 position:24% line:89% align:start
[breathing heavily]

00:02:01.144 --> 00:02:03.213 position:33% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

00:02:03.246 --> 00:02:05.849 position:35% line:89% align:start
[coughing]

00:02:13.189 --> 00:02:16.360 position:21% line:89% align:start
[breathing steadily]

00:02:17.294 --> 00:02:18.795 position:41% line:89% align:start
Anna...

00:02:20.264 --> 00:02:22.665 position:27% line:83% align:start
You're fine now.
That's all, ok?

00:02:22.699 --> 00:02:26.237 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm so glad. Thank you very
much doctor, thank you.

00:02:26.270 --> 00:02:30.174 position:27% line:83% align:start
Oh, I'm relieved.
Anna, how do you feel now?

00:02:30.207 --> 00:02:30.907 position:35% line:89% align:start
I am fine.

00:02:32.076 --> 00:02:34.777 position:24% line:83% align:start
It looked like you
were in so much pain.

00:02:34.811 --> 00:02:36.280 position:10% line:89% align:start
Didn't you have your inhaler?

00:02:38.449 --> 00:02:41.152 position:19% line:89% align:start
I cost you money again.

00:02:41.185 --> 00:02:43.354 position:19% line:89% align:start
No, why'd you say that?

00:02:43.387 --> 00:02:45.122 position:27% line:89% align:start
[doorbell rings]

00:02:46.924 --> 00:02:47.925 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hi girls. Miyoko.

00:02:49.160 --> 00:02:52.963 position:5% line:83% align:start
Anna left her school bag behind.
She also left her notebook.

00:02:52.997 --> 00:02:54.098 position:30% line:89% align:start
Why, thank you.

00:02:54.131 --> 00:02:58.836 position:13% line:83% align:start
We were nearby. If there's
anything else we can do...

00:02:58.869 --> 00:02:59.436 position:35% line:89% align:start
Miyoko...?

00:03:00.771 --> 00:03:03.440 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Yoriko] <i>Has Anna been</i>
 <i>getting along with all of you?</i>

00:03:03.474 --> 00:03:06.443 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>She doesn't tell me</i>
 <i>anything about school.</i>

00:03:06.477 --> 00:03:07.912 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Miyoko]
 <i>She's okay.</i>

00:03:07.945 --> 00:03:09.880 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>She's just very quiet...</i>

00:03:09.914 --> 00:03:12.316 position:10% line:89% align:start
Quiet? Mice make more noise!

00:03:12.349 --> 00:03:14.818 position:30% line:89% align:start
C'mon, stop it.

00:03:14.852 --> 00:03:17.821 position:13% line:83% align:start
It's not that she's quiet,
we're just loud.

00:03:17.855 --> 00:03:19.056 position:33% line:89% align:start
[girls laugh]

00:03:19.089 --> 00:03:21.459 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Miyoko]
 <i>Ok, take care. Bye.</i>

00:03:21.493 --> 00:03:24.795 position:13% line:83% align:start
Always worrying about you,
isn't she, your mother?

00:03:24.828 --> 00:03:27.998 position:24% line:89% align:start
[melancholic music]

00:03:28.032 --> 00:03:29.367 position:33% line:89% align:start
My mother...?

00:03:32.270 --> 00:03:35.973 position:7% line:83% align:start
She's probably cut herself off
from everyone at school.

00:03:36.006 --> 00:03:36.907 position:16% line:89% align:start
You know, in some cases,

00:03:36.941 --> 00:03:40.145 position:24% line:83% align:start
asthma attacks can
be related to stress.

00:03:40.178 --> 00:03:43.215 position:21% line:83% align:start
It doesn't help that
my husband travels a lot.

00:03:44.848 --> 00:03:49.019 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Yoriko] <i>He has to, for work.</i>
 <i>Maybe it's our fault.</i>

00:03:49.054 --> 00:03:50.522 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Doctor]
 <i>12 years old...</i>

00:03:50.555 --> 00:03:52.790 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>It's a difficult age.</i>

00:03:52.823 --> 00:03:55.427 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Have you noticed anything</i>
 <i>different about her?</i>

00:03:55.460 --> 00:04:00.798 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Yoriko] <i>Yes, she... she</i>
 <i>always has an ordinary face.</i>

00:04:00.831 --> 00:04:02.100 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Doctor]
 <i>Ordinary?</i>

00:04:02.133 --> 00:04:03.268 position:27% line:89% align:start
What do you mean?

00:04:06.338 --> 00:04:07.906 position:38% line:83% align:start
[sniffs]
I'm sorry.

00:04:10.141 --> 00:04:13.178 position:13% line:83% align:start
It's like she doesn't allow
her emotions to show.

00:04:14.879 --> 00:04:17.482 position:7% line:89% align:start
She used to be more expressive.

00:04:17.515 --> 00:04:21.519 position:16% line:83% align:start
But these days, her face
is almost... wooden.

00:04:21.553 --> 00:04:23.355 position:24% line:89% align:start
Not happy. Not sad.

00:04:24.356 --> 00:04:26.458 position:21% line:89% align:start
Just there. Maybe...

00:04:26.491 --> 00:04:29.894 position:24% line:83% align:start
maybe because we're
not related by blood.

00:04:29.928 --> 00:04:33.098 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Doctor] <i>It may be time to</i>
 <i>consider, like we discussed...</i>

00:04:33.131 --> 00:04:37.470 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>send her to your relatives</i>
 <i>for a while-a bit of fresh air.</i>

00:04:37.503 --> 00:04:40.972 position:30% line:89% align:start
[string music]

00:04:41.006 --> 00:04:45.311 position:27% line:5% align:start
[engine rumbling]

00:04:49.348 --> 00:04:50.882 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Yoriko]
 <i>Say, Anna...</i>

00:04:50.915 --> 00:04:51.916 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:04:51.950 --> 00:04:54.587 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Do you remember</i>
 <i>Uncle and Aunt Oiwa?</i>

00:04:54.620 --> 00:04:57.590 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>The air is very clean</i>
 <i>where they live.</i>

00:04:57.623 --> 00:04:59.425 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>The doctor says it'll</i>
 <i>help your condition</i>

00:04:59.458 --> 00:05:01.294 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>to spend a bit of time in a...</i>

00:05:01.327 --> 00:05:02.861 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>in a place like that.</i>

00:05:03.629 --> 00:05:05.264 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>I can't go with you, but</i>

00:05:05.298 --> 00:05:08.367 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'm sure they will</i>
 <i>take good care of you.</i>

00:05:10.603 --> 00:05:13.439 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>Be a good girl, eat well,</i>

00:05:13.472 --> 00:05:17.009 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>and you come back nice</i>
 <i>and happy, okay?</i>

00:05:17.043 --> 00:05:21.380 position:27% line:89% align:start
[peaceful music]

00:05:25.885 --> 00:05:29.221 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Anna sighs]
 <i>She whines like a goat.</i>

00:05:29.255 --> 00:05:33.426 position:30% line:89% align:start
[train rumbles]

00:05:50.076 --> 00:05:52.144 position:24% line:89% align:start
[door hisses open]

00:06:03.222 --> 00:06:05.559 position:30% line:89% align:start
[train rumbles]

00:06:05.592 --> 00:06:06.593 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Anna sighs]

00:06:13.400 --> 00:06:15.502 position:27% line:89% align:start
Oh. There she is.

00:06:16.203 --> 00:06:18.238 position:33% line:89% align:start
Oh! Anna, hi!

00:06:18.271 --> 00:06:19.573 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Anna gasps]

00:06:23.008 --> 00:06:24.177 position:33% line:89% align:start
Remember us?

00:06:24.211 --> 00:06:27.514 position:24% line:83% align:start
Yes. Well, actually
no, not really.

00:06:27.547 --> 00:06:30.484 position:16% line:83% align:start
Auntie told me about you.
I hope I'm not too much trouble.

00:06:30.517 --> 00:06:32.386 position:7% line:89% align:start
Thank you for looking after me.

00:06:34.421 --> 00:06:35.655 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's our pleasure.

00:06:36.423 --> 00:06:37.924 position:35% line:89% align:start
Her Auntie?

00:06:37.958 --> 00:06:39.426 position:27% line:89% align:start
She means Yoriko.

00:06:39.459 --> 00:06:40.594 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Kiyomasa Oiwa]
Ah.

00:06:42.996 --> 00:06:46.366 position:19% line:83% align:start
Here we go. Hop on in.
Sorry it's a bit of a clunker.

00:06:54.341 --> 00:06:56.943 position:7% line:89% align:start
We had to pick up a few things.

00:06:56.977 --> 00:06:58.145 position:21% line:89% align:start
I don't mind at all.

00:06:59.379 --> 00:07:02.015 position:13% line:83% align:start
Boy, this place has really
changed since I was here last.

00:07:02.048 --> 00:07:04.552 position:21% line:83% align:start
Look at all these new
stores that have opened up.

00:07:04.585 --> 00:07:08.723 position:13% line:83% align:start
Where we live it's nice and
relaxing. You'll love it there.

00:07:08.756 --> 00:07:10.558 position:30% line:83% align:start
Ever since they
built this highway,

00:07:10.591 --> 00:07:12.926 position:7% line:89% align:start
people stopped passing through.

00:07:24.772 --> 00:07:26.541 position:35% line:89% align:start
[thudding]

00:07:26.574 --> 00:07:29.577 position:24% line:89% align:start
[ripping, rattling]

00:07:29.610 --> 00:07:33.113 position:21% line:83% align:start
Anna, you all right?
That was just a little pothole.

00:07:33.147 --> 00:07:36.451 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:07:36.484 --> 00:07:37.984 position:13% line:89% align:start
So I hear you have asthma?

00:07:38.018 --> 00:07:39.320 position:35% line:89% align:start
Uh, yes...

00:07:39.353 --> 00:07:42.123 position:16% line:83% align:start
Air around here is sweet.
Fix you up in no time.

00:07:42.156 --> 00:07:44.392 position:27% line:89% align:start
[engine revving]

00:07:46.160 --> 00:07:50.097 position:35% line:89% align:start
[rumbling]

00:07:50.131 --> 00:07:51.299 position:7% line:89% align:start
Hey, it's beautiful, isn't it?

00:07:51.332 --> 00:07:54.202 position:13% line:83% align:start
I bet you wish your Auntie
could come up here and see it.

00:07:54.235 --> 00:07:55.603 position:10% line:89% align:start
What is that up on the hill?

00:07:57.104 --> 00:07:58.005 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>That thing on the cliff.</i>

00:07:58.039 --> 00:07:59.674 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Kiyomasa Oiwa]
 <i>Oh, that's a silo.</i>

00:07:59.707 --> 00:08:02.610 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>They use it to</i>
 <i>store feed for livestock.</i>

00:08:02.643 --> 00:08:05.379 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Hasn't been used</i>
 <i>in decades, though.</i>

00:08:05.413 --> 00:08:07.181 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Nowadays it's just a</i>
 <i>place where kids</i>

00:08:07.215 --> 00:08:08.983 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>kinda dare each other to go in.</i>

00:08:10.284 --> 00:08:13.154 position:21% line:83% align:start
Word is the place is
full of ghosts at night.

00:08:13.187 --> 00:08:15.289 position:33% line:83% align:start
Will you stop
trying to scare her!

00:08:15.323 --> 00:08:17.325 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Setsu]
 <i>He loves stories like that.</i>

00:08:17.358 --> 00:08:18.760 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Kiyomasa Oiwa]
 <i>In any case,</i>

00:08:18.794 --> 00:08:21.362 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>it's probably a good idea</i>
 <i>to stay away from that place.</i>

00:08:21.395 --> 00:08:23.064 position:16% line:89% align:start
[kids laughing, yelling]

00:08:25.233 --> 00:08:28.570 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Kiyomasa Oiwa] <i>Here we are!</i>
 <i>Your home away from home.</i>

00:08:30.304 --> 00:08:33.174 position:30% line:89% align:start
[engine idling]

00:08:33.207 --> 00:08:35.577 position:24% line:83% align:start
Hon-buns, will you
take this in for me?

00:08:35.611 --> 00:08:36.210 position:33% line:89% align:start
What's this?

00:08:37.144 --> 00:08:40.214 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Setsu]
 <i>Why would you accept this?</i>

00:08:40.249 --> 00:08:43.552 position:16% line:83% align:start
We couldn't possibly eat
all of it ourselves.

00:08:43.585 --> 00:08:47.356 position:13% line:83% align:start
He's always accepting gifts
without thinking...

00:08:49.791 --> 00:08:53.228 position:16% line:83% align:start
Our kids are all grown up
and moved out,

00:08:53.262 --> 00:08:54.596 position:16% line:89% align:start
so make yourself at home.

00:08:54.630 --> 00:08:55.731 position:41% line:89% align:start
Thanks.

00:08:55.764 --> 00:08:59.067 position:19% line:89% align:start
Now this goes where...?

00:08:59.101 --> 00:09:00.569 position:33% line:89% align:start
What a place.

00:09:10.178 --> 00:09:13.282 position:16% line:83% align:start
You must be thinking it's
an odd house we've got.

00:09:13.315 --> 00:09:15.350 position:5% line:89% align:start
No, I think your home is lovely.

00:09:15.384 --> 00:09:17.219 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Aunt Oiwa laughs]

00:09:17.252 --> 00:09:19.488 position:27% line:83% align:start
Flattery will get
you everywhere.

00:09:21.590 --> 00:09:22.759 position:24% line:89% align:start
Come on. Follow me.

00:09:22.792 --> 00:09:24.059 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'll show you where
you're staying.

00:09:25.460 --> 00:09:27.329 position:10% line:89% align:start
This was my daughter's room.

00:09:29.866 --> 00:09:32.267 position:30% line:83% align:start
It'd be sad to
get rid of everything,

00:09:32.301 --> 00:09:34.804 position:30% line:83% align:start
so I just left
it the way it was.

00:09:34.837 --> 00:09:36.138 position:33% line:89% align:start
I understand.

00:09:36.171 --> 00:09:38.307 position:19% line:83% align:start
She's a yoga instructor
in Tokyo now.

00:09:38.340 --> 00:09:39.742 position:16% line:89% align:start
Have you ever tried yoga?

00:09:41.176 --> 00:09:43.111 position:30% line:83% align:start
I'm thinking of
trying it myself.

00:09:44.212 --> 00:09:46.148 position:24% line:83% align:start
Oh, the closet and
shelves are empty,

00:09:46.181 --> 00:09:47.717 position:16% line:89% align:start
so feel free to use 'em.

00:09:48.551 --> 00:09:50.152 position:35% line:89% align:start
Thank you.

00:09:50.185 --> 00:09:51.186 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:09:57.827 --> 00:09:59.495 position:7% line:89% align:start
"Write and tell me how you are,

00:09:59.529 --> 00:10:02.765 position:19% line:83% align:start
or whatever you wish to
tell me about. Yoriko."

00:10:02.799 --> 00:10:05.401 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Setsu] Oh, how nice!
Postcards in this day and age.

00:10:05.435 --> 00:10:07.470 position:5% line:89% align:start
You should definitely write her.

00:10:07.503 --> 00:10:08.905 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Kiyomasa Oiwa]
 <i>Setsu, come here for a second!</i>

00:10:08.938 --> 00:10:10.273 position:41% line:89% align:start
Coming!

00:10:10.740 --> 00:10:12.375 position:30% line:89% align:start
He's so pushy.

00:10:13.176 --> 00:10:14.510 position:16% line:89% align:start
All right then, see you.

00:10:15.678 --> 00:10:16.713 position:33% line:89% align:start
[door shuts]

00:10:16.746 --> 00:10:19.616 position:19% line:89% align:start
[footsteps moving away]

00:10:20.650 --> 00:10:22.452 position:5% line:89% align:start
Smells like someone else's home.

00:10:31.761 --> 00:10:32.762 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:10:33.696 --> 00:10:36.633 position:21% line:89% align:start
[engine in distance]

00:10:36.666 --> 00:10:38.201 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:10:38.234 --> 00:10:39.435 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>Wow.</i>

00:10:40.503 --> 00:10:44.775 position:27% line:89% align:start
[peaceful music]

00:10:44.808 --> 00:10:47.745 position:27% line:89% align:start
[engine chugging]

00:10:51.649 --> 00:10:53.851 position:27% line:89% align:start
[birds chirping]

00:10:55.886 --> 00:10:57.655 position:27% line:89% align:start
Feels wonderful.

00:10:57.688 --> 00:10:59.957 position:27% line:89% align:start
[breathes deeply]

00:10:59.990 --> 00:11:01.659 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>I've arrived safely.</i>

00:11:01.692 --> 00:11:03.661 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>It's quite nice here.</i>

00:11:03.694 --> 00:11:06.262 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Mr. and Mrs. Oiwa are</i>
 <i>both very kind.</i>

00:11:19.443 --> 00:11:22.379 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Setsu] <i>These are delicious,</i>
 <i>you should try one.</i>

00:11:22.413 --> 00:11:25.215 position:16% line:83% align:start
Sorry, sweetie, my hands
are full right now.

00:11:25.249 --> 00:11:28.752 position:13% line:83% align:start
Hello... I'm gonna to go to
the post office, okay?

