Hey, Anna!
Where did you go?

00:26:25.260 --> 00:26:26.662 position:33% line:83% align:start
I was looking
all over for you.

00:26:26.696 --> 00:26:29.331 position:27% line:83% align:start
Didn't know where
you went! Oh! Your wish!

00:26:29.364 --> 00:26:31.232 position:30% line:83% align:start
- [Anna grasps]
- Let's see now...

00:26:31.266 --> 00:26:33.569 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Nobuko] "I wish for a
normal life everyday."

00:26:35.203 --> 00:26:35.838 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:26:36.505 --> 00:26:37.473 position:38% line:89% align:start
"Normal"?

00:26:37.506 --> 00:26:39.342 position:13% line:89% align:start
What do you mean by normal?

00:26:39.375 --> 00:26:40.710 position:35% line:89% align:start
Um, well...

00:26:40.743 --> 00:26:41.577 position:30% line:89% align:start
You see, um...

00:26:42.511 --> 00:26:44.614 position:13% line:89% align:start
I can't believe your eyes!

00:26:44.647 --> 00:26:46.147 position:41% line:83% align:start
[girl]
What's going on?

00:26:46.182 --> 00:26:48.517 position:33% line:83% align:start
Anna's eyes.
They're sort of blue!

00:26:48.551 --> 00:26:49.819 position:10% line:89% align:start
It's actually really pretty!

00:26:49.852 --> 00:26:51.754 position:16% line:83% align:start
- Almost like a foreign-
- Leave me alone already!

00:26:51.787 --> 00:26:52.822 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:26:53.522 --> 00:26:54.757 position:33% line:89% align:start
You fat pig!

00:26:54.790 --> 00:26:55.791 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Nobuko gasps]

00:26:57.593 --> 00:26:58.761 position:30% line:89% align:start
Did she say...?

00:26:58.794 --> 00:27:00.496 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:27:00.529 --> 00:27:02.832 position:21% line:89% align:start
Uh... I, I didn't...

00:27:02.865 --> 00:27:03.432 position:47% line:89% align:start
Hm.

00:27:04.500 --> 00:27:06.669 position:27% line:83% align:start
Now I see why you
wish to be normal.

00:27:08.671 --> 00:27:09.873 position:33% line:89% align:start
So pathetic.

00:27:09.906 --> 00:27:12.375 position:24% line:83% align:start
You shouldn't even
pretend to be normal.

00:27:12.408 --> 00:27:15.912 position:24% line:83% align:start
After all, you look
like just what you are.

00:27:18.949 --> 00:27:21.517 position:24% line:83% align:start
Hey, what d'you say
we just drop it?

00:27:21.550 --> 00:27:23.720 position:19% line:83% align:start
And you could come out
with us next week or-

00:27:23.754 --> 00:27:25.421 position:33% line:83% align:start
[girls gasp]
[Anna crying]

00:27:25.454 --> 00:27:26.957 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Nobuko]
Anna! Wait!

00:27:26.990 --> 00:27:30.894 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Anna crying]

00:27:36.833 --> 00:27:39.469 position:24% line:89% align:start
[melancholic music]

00:27:39.503 --> 00:27:40.904 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>Like just what I am...</i>

00:27:44.007 --> 00:27:47.611 position:35% line:89% align:start
[coughing]

00:27:47.644 --> 00:27:51.648 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:27:54.918 --> 00:27:58.488 position:38% line:89% align:start
[crying]d

00:28:04.761 --> 00:28:06.630 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>Like just what I am...</i>

00:28:09.366 --> 00:28:11.802 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>Ugly, stupid,</i>

00:28:13.437 --> 00:28:14.705 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>moody,</i>

00:28:17.607 --> 00:28:19.443 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>unpleasant...</i>

00:28:22.046 --> 00:28:24.214 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>That's why I hate myself.</i>

00:28:26.683 --> 00:28:27.617 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>That's why everyone...</i>

00:28:29.419 --> 00:28:31.455 position:19% line:77% align:start
How long do you think
we have left to live?

00:28:31.488 --> 00:28:32.857 position:7% line:83% align:start
- Typically in this situation,
- [baby crying]

00:28:32.890 --> 00:28:35.659 position:19% line:83% align:start
the child usually goes
to an aunt or an uncle.

00:28:35.692 --> 00:28:37.360 position:38% line:83% align:start
[man #2]
I told you, we can't.

00:28:37.394 --> 00:28:39.663 position:10% line:83% align:start
I thought that we had already
settled this matter.

00:28:39.697 --> 00:28:41.666 position:19% line:83% align:start
We're not blaming you.
It's just that

00:28:41.699 --> 00:28:43.533 position:21% line:83% align:start
when you think about
looking after a child,

00:28:43.567 --> 00:28:45.569 position:5% line:83% align:start
- Look! I told you many times...
- you're the obvious choice...

00:28:45.602 --> 00:28:46.771 position:38% line:83% align:start
[man #3]
it's not a matter of money.

00:28:46.804 --> 00:28:48.305 position:38% line:83% align:start
[man #2]
Sure, I feel bad for her, but...

00:28:48.338 --> 00:28:50.340 position:38% line:83% align:start
[man #1]
But nothing. Please, reconsider.

00:28:52.777 --> 00:28:54.912 position:24% line:89% align:start
[melancholic music]

00:29:09.894 --> 00:29:11.829 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'd better get home.

00:29:11.863 --> 00:29:13.297 position:27% line:89% align:start
[insects buzzing]

00:29:13.331 --> 00:29:14.332 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:29:36.687 --> 00:29:38.556 position:16% line:89% align:start
Did someone row it here?

00:29:40.792 --> 00:29:41.793 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:29:52.537 --> 00:29:53.538 position:33% line:83% align:start
- [splashing]
- Ah!

00:29:56.742 --> 00:29:59.111 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:29:59.144 --> 00:30:02.047 position:30% line:83% align:start
[wood creaking,
water splashing]

00:30:02.080 --> 00:30:04.348 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:30:07.786 --> 00:30:10.088 position:38% line:89% align:start
Uh... ah!

00:30:10.122 --> 00:30:14.325 position:35% line:83% align:start
[splashing]
[grunting]

00:30:21.700 --> 00:30:22.734 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:30:33.745 --> 00:30:35.447 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:30:35.480 --> 00:30:37.082 position:30% line:83% align:start
[wood creaking]
[gasps]

00:30:37.115 --> 00:30:38.350 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's stuck!

00:30:38.817 --> 00:30:42.454 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:30:45.424 --> 00:30:46.992 position:16% line:89% align:start
Throw me the rope! Hurry!

00:30:47.025 --> 00:30:48.360 position:44% line:89% align:start
Rope?

00:30:51.064 --> 00:30:53.398 position:30% line:83% align:start
- [gate bangs]
- Quickly!

00:30:53.432 --> 00:30:55.601 position:38% line:83% align:start
[banging]
[grunts]

00:31:03.742 --> 00:31:08.614 position:41% line:83% align:start
[bangs]
[groans]

00:31:10.216 --> 00:31:12.584 position:38% line:83% align:start
[panting]
[splashing]

00:31:19.225 --> 00:31:22.662 position:27% line:89% align:start
[peaceful music]

00:31:24.130 --> 00:31:25.397 position:33% line:89% align:start
Are you okay?

00:31:26.866 --> 00:31:30.003 position:7% line:89% align:start
Um, yeah... good... are you...

00:31:31.804 --> 00:31:33.740 position:30% line:83% align:start
- Are you real?
- Wait. Shh.

00:31:33.773 --> 00:31:35.174 position:30% line:83% align:start
Let's not have
anyone hear us.

00:31:36.542 --> 00:31:39.412 position:24% line:83% align:start
In my dreams I saw
a girl, just like you.

00:31:40.647 --> 00:31:42.415 position:35% line:89% align:start
Dreams? Hm.

00:31:46.886 --> 00:31:48.087 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:31:49.722 --> 00:31:50.757 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:31:55.895 --> 00:31:56.963 position:35% line:89% align:start
Thank you.

00:32:01.601 --> 00:32:02.835 position:27% line:89% align:start
It's not a dream.

00:32:09.109 --> 00:32:10.910 position:27% line:89% align:start
What's your name?

00:32:11.878 --> 00:32:12.947 position:44% line:89% align:start
Anna.

00:32:12.980 --> 00:32:16.884 position:16% line:83% align:start
Anna. That's a nice name.
I hope we can be friends.

00:32:16.917 --> 00:32:17.784 position:21% line:89% align:start
Would you like that?

00:32:21.855 --> 00:32:23.723 position:10% line:89% align:start
Have you seen me before now?

00:32:24.724 --> 00:32:25.859 position:41% line:89% align:start
Uh huh.

00:32:26.193 --> 00:32:27.593 position:41% line:89% align:start
Often.

00:32:28.594 --> 00:32:31.231 position:41% line:83% align:start
Really?
But, I just got here.

00:32:31.265 --> 00:32:32.900 position:33% line:83% align:start
How long have
you been here?

00:32:32.933 --> 00:32:34.001 position:7% line:89% align:start
I've been here for a long time.

00:32:34.034 --> 00:32:35.169 position:30% line:83% align:start
- [door opens]
- I-

00:32:37.171 --> 00:32:40.941 position:24% line:89% align:start
[muffled laughter]

00:32:40.975 --> 00:32:42.176 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Anna gasps]

00:32:50.017 --> 00:32:53.120 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Mother] Look at this view,
the marsh at night.

00:32:53.153 --> 00:32:54.922 position:30% line:89% align:start
How beautiful.

00:32:54.955 --> 00:32:56.757 position:24% line:83% align:start
Say, let's go down
and get a closer look.

00:32:56.790 --> 00:32:59.526 position:16% line:83% align:start
- Wouldn't that be nice?
- [Nan] Please, madam.

00:32:59.560 --> 00:33:01.228 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Mother]
I know...

00:33:01.261 --> 00:33:03.097 position:5% line:89% align:start
By the way, where is that child?

00:33:03.130 --> 00:33:05.232 position:44% line:83% align:start
[Nan]
Was she not in her room again?

00:33:09.970 --> 00:33:11.138 position:24% line:89% align:start
[melancholic music]

00:33:11.172 --> 00:33:13.007 position:24% line:89% align:start
I need to get back.

00:33:13.040 --> 00:33:15.542 position:7% line:83% align:start
- Were they talking about you?
- Yes.

00:33:17.644 --> 00:33:21.316 position:16% line:83% align:start
At this hour, I'm usually
tucked up in bed, asleep.

00:33:21.349 --> 00:33:22.950 position:35% line:89% align:start
[giggling]

00:33:22.983 --> 00:33:25.519 position:13% line:89% align:start
Come on, I'll row you back.

00:33:26.887 --> 00:33:27.721 position:10% line:89% align:start
So it actually was your boat.

00:33:29.057 --> 00:33:31.792 position:16% line:83% align:start
Of course! I left it for
you on purpose.

00:33:36.331 --> 00:33:38.732 position:13% line:83% align:start
But I thought you'd be able
to row a little better.

00:33:38.766 --> 00:33:39.767 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:33:41.136 --> 00:33:44.072 position:35% line:83% align:start
Honestly...
I thought I could too.

00:33:46.775 --> 00:33:48.943 position:27% line:83% align:start
You know, you're
my precious secret.

00:33:50.211 --> 00:33:53.681 position:5% line:83% align:start
I haven't told anyone about you,
and I never will.

00:33:55.050 --> 00:33:57.652 position:21% line:83% align:start
If someone finds out,
they'll only spoil it.

00:34:04.726 --> 00:34:07.295 position:33% line:83% align:start
Please, Anna.
Promise me something.

00:34:08.897 --> 00:34:11.066 position:13% line:89% align:start
That we'll remain a secret.

00:34:11.099 --> 00:34:12.233 position:38% line:89% align:start
Forever.

00:34:16.704 --> 00:34:17.705 position:38% line:89% align:start
Forever.

00:34:18.273 --> 00:34:21.109 position:27% line:89% align:start
[uplifting music]

00:34:35.257 --> 00:34:39.028 position:24% line:89% align:start
[insects chirping]

00:34:47.303 --> 00:34:48.304 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:34:49.338 --> 00:34:50.638 position:38% line:89% align:start
[scoffs]

00:34:52.241 --> 00:34:53.242 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:35:02.718 --> 00:35:04.353 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Mrs. Kadoya]
 <i>I tell you, it was awful.</i>

00:35:04.386 --> 00:35:06.722 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>She came home</i>
 <i>crying her eyes out!</i>

00:35:06.755 --> 00:35:08.023 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Setsu]
 <i>Wait, Anna did what?</i>

00:35:08.057 --> 00:35:11.260 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Mrs. Kadoya] <i>She called</i>
 <i>her a fat pig! My daughter!</i>

00:35:11.293 --> 00:35:12.294 position:35% line:89% align:start
My, oh my!

00:35:13.963 --> 00:35:17.900 position:13% line:83% align:start
And she pulled out a knife,
can you imagine?! The horror!

00:35:17.933 --> 00:35:19.068 position:7% line:89% align:start
Actually, I can't imagine that.

00:35:19.101 --> 00:35:22.171 position:13% line:83% align:start
Perhaps you should hear it
from the reprobate herself.

00:35:22.204 --> 00:35:23.739 position:19% line:89% align:start
So bring her out, now!

00:35:25.107 --> 00:35:26.809 position:19% line:83% align:start
Sorry, it doesn't look
like she's home just yet.

00:35:26.842 --> 00:35:27.743 position:44% line:89% align:start
Well!

00:35:27.776 --> 00:35:28.944 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Mrs. Kadoya]
 <i>I'm not surprised.</i>

00:35:28.978 --> 00:35:32.248 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>She's a delinquent,</i>
 <i>out and about this late!</i>

00:35:32.281 --> 00:35:35.885 position:13% line:83% align:start
And you two aren't exactly
what you call blameless.

00:35:35.918 --> 00:35:38.087 position:16% line:83% align:start
You should keep a closer
eye on that girl!

00:35:38.120 --> 00:35:39.221 position:33% line:83% align:start
[door slams]
[Setsu sighs]

00:35:41.291 --> 00:35:43.260 position:16% line:89% align:start
Take this. It's dark out.

00:35:43.293 --> 00:35:44.760 position:30% line:89% align:start
No, thank you.

00:35:44.793 --> 00:35:45.362 position:38% line:89% align:start
[scoffs]

00:35:46.795 --> 00:35:48.931 position:21% line:83% align:start
Unbelievable! What if
something were to happen

00:35:48.964 --> 00:35:51.000 position:16% line:83% align:start
to one of our local kids?
Oh!

00:35:51.033 --> 00:35:52.435 position:33% line:83% align:start
And he calls
himself a carpenter.

00:35:52.469 --> 00:35:55.172 position:24% line:83% align:start
So what if she's a
bit late getting home!

00:35:55.205 --> 00:35:56.906 position:38% line:83% align:start
Now, now,
don't get all riled up.

00:35:56.939 --> 00:36:00.310 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Setsu] How dare she call that
child a delinquent!

00:36:00.343 --> 00:36:02.078 position:24% line:89% align:start
Hup, there she is.

00:36:02.946 --> 00:36:04.214 position:44% line:89% align:start
Anna!

00:36:05.081 --> 00:36:06.183 position:27% line:89% align:start
It's not quite...

00:36:06.216 --> 00:36:09.785 position:13% line:83% align:start
Were you listening to that?
Don't you worry about it.

00:36:11.821 --> 00:36:14.257 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm sure you two will
make up somehow.

00:36:14.291 --> 00:36:16.860 position:16% line:83% align:start
All right, go take a bath
and have some dinner.

00:36:16.893 --> 00:36:17.994 position:41% line:89% align:start
Thanks.

00:36:18.028 --> 00:36:21.264 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Kiyomasa Oiwa] Or...
maybe dinner before the bath?

00:36:21.298 --> 00:36:22.332 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Setsu]
It hardly matters.

00:36:24.100 --> 00:36:27.170 position:19% line:83% align:start
But "fat pig" may have
been a bit harsh, eh?

00:36:27.204 --> 00:36:29.172 position:38% line:83% align:start
[laughs]
That's for sure.

00:36:29.206 --> 00:36:30.807 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Setsu]
It's not that funny.

00:36:34.978 --> 00:36:36.346 position:27% line:89% align:start
[insects buzzing]

00:36:45.489 --> 00:36:47.357 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>Another letter from home.</i>

00:36:49.159 --> 00:36:52.929 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>She might as well just write,</i>
 <i>"Worrying. Like always."</i>

00:36:56.334 --> 00:36:58.902 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Setsu]
 <i>Anna! Watermelon!</i>

00:36:59.970 --> 00:37:03.106 position:30% line:89% align:start
[clock ticking]

00:37:04.107 --> 00:37:05.875 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Setsu]
 <i>Anna?</i>

00:37:09.045 --> 00:37:11.848 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>Two hours until high tide...</i>

00:37:13.251 --> 00:37:17.288 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:37:28.466 --> 00:37:31.002 position:30% line:83% align:start
[wood creaking,
water splashing]

00:37:31.035 --> 00:37:32.103 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:37:56.160 --> 00:37:58.963 position:13% line:89% align:start
Hop in. I've got a picnic!

00:37:58.996 --> 00:38:01.165 position:10% line:89% align:start
I brought juice and cookies.

00:38:01.198 --> 00:38:04.001 position:19% line:89% align:start
A picnic? At this hour?

00:38:04.035 --> 00:38:07.439 position:16% line:83% align:start
Why not? Let's go to the
far side of the cove.

00:38:07.472 --> 00:38:10.975 position:27% line:89% align:start
[peaceful music]

00:38:19.484 --> 00:38:21.420 position:24% line:83% align:start
You are much better
than me at rowing.

00:38:23.622 --> 00:38:25.890 position:27% line:83% align:start
Anyone can do it.
Let me show you.

00:38:25.923 --> 00:38:27.024 position:27% line:89% align:start
Come sit with me.

00:38:27.058 --> 00:38:28.060 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:38:32.064 --> 00:38:33.332 position:24% line:89% align:start
You're doing fine.

00:38:40.939 --> 00:38:43.275 position:13% line:89% align:start
Remember I said last night

00:38:43.308 --> 00:38:45.944 position:7% line:89% align:start
that you're my precious secret?

00:38:47.212 --> 00:38:51.049 position:19% line:83% align:start
I remember. And I love
that you're my secret.

00:38:51.083 --> 00:38:52.351 position:38% line:89% align:start
I'm glad.

00:38:52.384 --> 00:38:53.552 position:38% line:89% align:start
Wait! No!

00:38:53.585 --> 00:38:55.220 position:35% line:89% align:start
You let go!

00:38:55.253 --> 00:38:56.521 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:39:00.625 --> 00:39:03.095 position:27% line:89% align:start
Good! Very good.

00:39:07.199 --> 00:39:10.402 position:10% line:83% align:start
You know... you still haven't
told me your name.

00:39:12.337 --> 00:39:14.039 position:35% line:89% align:start
That's odd.

00:39:14.072 --> 00:39:15.040 position:13% line:89% align:start
I thought you already knew.

00:39:16.542 --> 00:39:19.545 position:19% line:83% align:start
Marnie! That's my name,
don't wear it out.

00:39:19.579 --> 00:39:21.246 position:38% line:89% align:start
[giggles]

00:39:21.980 --> 00:39:23.248 position:24% line:89% align:start
Please be careful.

00:39:32.392 --> 00:39:34.594 position:24% line:89% align:start
Go ahead, just row.

00:39:51.277 --> 00:39:53.946 position:10% line:83% align:start
There's all sorts of things I
want to know about you.

00:39:55.548 --> 00:39:59.252 position:21% line:83% align:start
But, I don't wish to
find out too fast.

00:39:59.285 --> 00:40:01.554 position:24% line:83% align:start
Let's take it slow
as we go along.

00:40:03.556 --> 00:40:04.657 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'll tell you what we'll do.

00:40:06.459 --> 00:40:09.595 position:5% line:83% align:start
You and I - we'll ask each other
three questions every night.

00:40:09.629 --> 00:40:11.164 position:16% line:89% align:start
What do you say to that?

00:40:11.197 --> 00:40:12.398 position:33% line:89% align:start
Sounds good.

00:40:12.432 --> 00:40:14.600 position:13% line:83% align:start
All right then. Here we go.
First question.

00:40:14.634 --> 00:40:16.335 position:19% line:83% align:start
What brings you here to
our little village,

00:40:16.369 --> 00:40:18.471 position:24% line:83% align:start
and how long do you
plan on staying?

00:40:19.706 --> 00:40:21.574 position:7% line:89% align:start
I have something called asthma.

00:40:21.608 --> 00:40:24.310 position:27% line:83% align:start
And this doctor,
Doctor Yamashita,

00:40:24.343 --> 00:40:27.380 position:10% line:83% align:start
he said I should go somewhere
with clean air for a while.

00:40:27.413 --> 00:40:29.315 position:7% line:89% align:start
Even if I have to skip school.

00:40:29.348 --> 00:40:31.017 position:24% line:89% align:start
Oh no, you're ill?

00:40:31.050 --> 00:40:33.152 position:7% line:89% align:start
Don't worry. I'm fine, honest.

00:40:33.186 --> 00:40:34.320 position:33% line:83% align:start
But my Auntie
thought it best

00:40:34.353 --> 00:40:37.558 position:16% line:83% align:start
that I came here and stay
with her relatives, the Oiwas.

00:40:37.591 --> 00:40:38.725 position:33% line:89% align:start
Who's Auntie?

00:40:38.759 --> 00:40:41.294 position:27% line:83% align:start
Now it's my turn
to ask a question!

00:40:41.328 --> 00:40:44.298 position:21% line:83% align:start
So how is it that you
live in that mansion?

00:40:44.331 --> 00:40:46.633 position:19% line:83% align:start
I've lived there since
I was two years old.

00:40:46.667 --> 00:40:49.202 position:13% line:89% align:start
Myself, Nan and the maids.

00:40:49.236 --> 00:40:50.036 position:33% line:89% align:start
Here, juice.

00:40:51.371 --> 00:40:54.341 position:21% line:83% align:start
Where are your mother
and father? Where are they?

00:40:54.374 --> 00:40:56.510 position:33% line:83% align:start
They can only
come sometimes.

00:40:56.543 --> 00:40:58.445 position:10% line:89% align:start
They're very busy with work.

00:40:58.479 --> 00:40:59.480 position:41% line:89% align:start
Uh huh.

00:40:59.513 --> 00:41:02.616 position:24% line:83% align:start
My second question.
Tell me, who's Auntie?

00:41:04.351 --> 00:41:06.420 position:41% line:83% align:start
[sighs]
She's my guardian.

00:41:06.453 --> 00:41:08.255 position:27% line:83% align:start
You know, kind of
like a mother, but

00:41:08.288 --> 00:41:11.692 position:7% line:83% align:start
I guess one who can get rid of
me when I'm being a total pain.

00:41:11.725 --> 00:41:13.494 position:27% line:89% align:start
What do you mean?

00:41:13.527 --> 00:41:16.063 position:7% line:89% align:start
I'll explain more another time.

00:41:16.096 --> 00:41:18.232 position:10% line:89% align:start
All right, it's my turn now.

00:41:18.265 --> 00:41:19.733 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>How many siblings do you have?</i>

00:41:19.766 --> 00:41:21.568 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Marnie]
 <i>None. I'm an only child.</i>

00:41:21.602 --> 00:41:23.504 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>I see, you too...</i>

00:41:23.537 --> 00:41:24.538 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Marnie]
 <i>Why do you ask?</i>

00:41:26.106 --> 00:41:28.342 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>Oh, it's nothing.</i>

00:41:28.375 --> 00:41:29.643 position:21% line:89% align:start
Don't you ever wonder

00:41:29.676 --> 00:41:32.346 position:19% line:83% align:start
what it's like to have
brothers or sisters?

00:41:32.379 --> 00:41:35.750 position:44% line:83% align:start
I do.
It's fun to imagine that...

00:41:35.783 --> 00:41:37.785 position:35% line:83% align:start
All right,
question number three.

00:41:37.819 --> 00:41:41.522 position:30% line:83% align:start
What's it like
living at the Oiwas?

00:41:41.556 --> 00:41:42.690 position:35% line:89% align:start
The Oiwas?

00:41:44.659 --> 00:41:46.093 position:35% line:89% align:start
[crackling]

00:41:46.126 --> 00:41:47.461 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>Huh...</i>

00:41:47.495 --> 00:41:48.663 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>How strange...</i>

00:41:50.665 --> 00:41:51.699 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>I can't...</i>

00:41:51.733 --> 00:41:53.033 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>quite remember...</i>

00:41:55.470 --> 00:41:58.606 position:33% line:89% align:start
[slow music]

00:42:24.465 --> 00:42:26.834 position:27% line:89% align:start
[insects buzzing]

00:42:27.802 --> 00:42:29.203 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:42:30.872 --> 00:42:32.106 position:41% line:89% align:start
Marnie?

00:42:35.543 --> 00:42:36.678 position:41% line:89% align:start
Marnie!

00:42:36.711 --> 00:42:37.779 position:44% line:89% align:start
Anna!

00:42:39.414 --> 00:42:40.682 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:42:40.715 --> 00:42:43.585 position:30% line:83% align:start
There you are.
Where did you go?

00:42:43.618 --> 00:42:46.220 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Marnie whimpering]

00:42:47.322 --> 00:42:48.489 position:41% line:89% align:start
Marnie?

00:42:53.729 --> 00:42:55.631 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm fine now, but you
suddenly disappeared

00:42:55.664 --> 00:42:57.800 position:21% line:83% align:start
and I was looking for
you everywhere.

00:42:57.833 --> 00:42:58.968 position:16% line:89% align:start
But I didn't go anywhere.

00:42:59.001 --> 00:43:03.706 position:16% line:83% align:start
I was just thinking about
the answer to your question...

00:43:03.739 --> 00:43:05.139 position:41% line:89% align:start
Wait...

00:43:05.774 --> 00:43:07.208 position:33% line:89% align:start
What was it?

00:43:07.241 --> 00:43:08.276 position:38% line:89% align:start
[giggles]

00:43:08.309 --> 00:43:10.446 position:10% line:89% align:start
It's okay, it doesn't matter.

00:43:10.479 --> 00:43:13.482 position:24% line:83% align:start
I really should get
going home anyhow.

00:43:13.515 --> 00:43:14.883 position:24% line:89% align:start
Because tonight...

00:43:14.917 --> 00:43:16.250 position:21% line:89% align:start
Hey! I have an idea!

00:43:18.754 --> 00:43:21.557 position:33% line:83% align:start
No no no no,
I really can't!

00:43:21.590 --> 00:43:23.359 position:24% line:83% align:start
Parties just really
aren't my thing.

00:43:23.392 --> 00:43:24.660 position:33% line:89% align:start
Don't worry.

00:43:25.728 --> 00:43:27.663 position:13% line:89% align:start
I have another great idea.

00:43:33.502 --> 00:43:34.603 position:38% line:89% align:start
Perfect.

00:43:35.971 --> 00:43:38.841 position:30% line:83% align:start
[wood creaking,
water splashing]

00:43:42.645 --> 00:43:44.948 position:33% line:83% align:start
[talking and
laughing in distance]

00:43:44.981 --> 00:43:47.616 position:30% line:89% align:start
[string music]

00:43:50.486 --> 00:43:52.856 position:27% line:89% align:start
[crowd chatting]

00:44:02.832 --> 00:44:04.500 position:16% line:89% align:start
I swear that it happened.

00:44:04.533 --> 00:44:06.235 position:33% line:83% align:start
I have a hard
time believing that.

00:44:16.613 --> 00:44:17.379 position:33% line:89% align:start
[door opens]

00:44:17.413 --> 00:44:18.882 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:44:18.915 --> 00:44:23.486 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry. Did you wait long?
I had trouble getting away.

00:44:23.520 --> 00:44:24.621 position:41% line:89% align:start
Marnie!

00:44:25.555 --> 00:44:27.457 position:38% line:83% align:start
[giggles]
What do you think?

00:44:28.425 --> 00:44:29.659 position:33% line:89% align:start
It's pretty.

00:44:30.727 --> 00:44:33.329 position:27% line:83% align:start
Here. I borrowed
Nan's shawl for you.

00:44:33.363 --> 00:44:35.365 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'll be scolded again.
[giggles]

00:44:35.398 --> 00:44:36.933 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm not sure this
is a good idea.

00:44:36.966 --> 00:44:39.002 position:16% line:83% align:start
I have a plan. I already
spoke to my dad.

00:44:39.035 --> 00:44:40.837 position:19% line:89% align:start
Come on. It'll be fun.

00:44:46.609 --> 00:44:47.777 position:35% line:89% align:start
Young lady.

00:44:48.878 --> 00:44:51.681 position:30% line:83% align:start
I believe it is
past your bedtime.

00:44:51.715 --> 00:44:54.551 position:33% line:83% align:start
And who might
this little girl be?

00:44:56.886 --> 00:44:59.023 position:16% line:89% align:start
That shawl belongs to me.

00:44:59.056 --> 00:45:00.256 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:45:00.924 --> 00:45:02.525 position:35% line:83% align:start
- Upstairs!
- Ah!

00:45:03.359 --> 00:45:04.461 position:27% line:89% align:start
Wait right there!

00:45:05.829 --> 00:45:06.830 position:35% line:89% align:start
Come back!

00:45:18.374 --> 00:45:21.712 position:30% line:83% align:start
Marnie, you are
nothing but trouble.

00:45:21.746 --> 00:45:23.981 position:13% line:89% align:start
Let's make a break for it!

00:45:24.014 --> 00:45:24.882 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:45:26.817 --> 00:45:28.284 position:41% line:89% align:start
Marnie!

00:45:28.318 --> 00:45:29.352 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Marnie grunts]

00:45:29.385 --> 00:45:30.553 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Nan groans]

00:45:30.588 --> 00:45:31.789 position:35% line:89% align:start
[jingling]

00:45:32.690 --> 00:45:33.791 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:45:34.992 --> 00:45:37.027 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Nan groaning]

00:45:37.661 --> 00:45:38.763 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:45:41.699 --> 00:45:44.635 position:44% line:83% align:start
[Nan]
 <i>Marnie! Open this door!</i>

00:45:44.668 --> 00:45:46.504 position:21% line:89% align:start
Brilliant! Let's go.

00:45:46.537 --> 00:45:49.340 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Nan] <i>This is no way for a</i>
 <i>young lady to behave!</i>

00:45:49.373 --> 00:45:51.575 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>This is no way for</i>
 <i>anyone to behave!</i>

00:45:51.609 --> 00:45:52.810 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:45:57.615 --> 00:46:01.452 position:13% line:83% align:start
Everybody! I'd like you to
meet a lovely flower girl!

00:46:01.485 --> 00:46:03.487 position:24% line:83% align:start
- [crowd clapping]
- A guest of my daughter.

00:46:03.521 --> 00:46:05.022 position:44% line:83% align:start
[man]
Ah, a flower girl.

00:46:05.055 --> 00:46:06.357 position:41% line:83% align:start
[woman]
That one must be Marnie.

00:46:06.390 --> 00:46:08.626 position:44% line:83% align:start
[man]
She's as pretty as her mother.

00:46:08.659 --> 00:46:11.962 position:7% line:83% align:start
Oh, welcome... May I please buy
one of those flowers?

00:46:13.531 --> 00:46:14.665 position:35% line:89% align:start
My mother.

00:46:22.673 --> 00:46:25.911 position:10% line:89% align:start
Hello, my dear little witch.

00:46:25.944 --> 00:46:26.845 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckles]

00:46:26.878 --> 00:46:29.981 position:30% line:83% align:start
A witch, ah-ha.
It takes one to know one.

00:46:30.015 --> 00:46:31.582 position:35% line:89% align:start
[all laugh]

00:46:31.615 --> 00:46:33.717 position:30% line:89% align:start
Uh, well, uh...

00:46:36.955 --> 00:46:39.623 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:46:39.657 --> 00:46:43.628 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'd like one please.
One for good fortune.

00:46:43.662 --> 00:46:47.498 position:16% line:83% align:start
Would someone kindly pay
for my pretty flower? Anyone?

00:46:47.531 --> 00:46:49.801 position:27% line:89% align:start
[crowd chatting]

00:46:49.835 --> 00:46:51.770 position:7% line:89% align:start
If it is the witch's command...

00:46:53.071 --> 00:46:55.040 position:19% line:89% align:start
I'll have one as well.

00:46:55.073 --> 00:46:57.876 position:19% line:83% align:start
- One for good fortune.
- Two for double the luck.

00:46:57.909 --> 00:46:59.477 position:33% line:83% align:start
- And for me!
- Me too!

00:46:59.511 --> 00:47:01.546 position:30% line:89% align:start
[bright music]

00:47:01.580 --> 00:47:02.881 position:30% line:89% align:start
Ah, it's begun.

00:47:03.849 --> 00:47:05.383 position:13% line:89% align:start
I could use a bit of luck.

00:47:05.417 --> 00:47:08.453 position:16% line:89% align:start
[crowd talking, laughing]

00:47:08.486 --> 00:47:09.554 position:41% line:89% align:start
Sorry!

00:47:09.588 --> 00:47:10.622 position:24% line:89% align:start
My luck's run out!

00:47:26.138 --> 00:47:28.874 position:21% line:83% align:start
Come on and take one,
this could be your lucky day!

00:47:28.907 --> 00:47:29.674 position:41% line:89% align:start
May I?

00:47:30.442 --> 00:47:34.013 position:24% line:89% align:start
[laughing, talking]

00:47:46.025 --> 00:47:47.459 position:35% line:89% align:start
Young lady.

00:47:47.492 --> 00:47:49.494 position:21% line:89% align:start
To your good health.

00:47:50.495 --> 00:47:53.498 position:13% line:89% align:start
Oh... thank you very much.

00:48:11.884 --> 00:48:13.052 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:48:13.085 --> 00:48:14.186 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's wine?

00:48:19.091 --> 00:48:22.194 position:27% line:89% align:start
[insects buzzing]

00:48:22.228 --> 00:48:23.963 position:33% line:89% align:start
[door opens]

00:48:26.198 --> 00:48:27.867 position:16% line:89% align:start
Anna, are you awake yet?

00:48:28.834 --> 00:48:30.002 position:38% line:89% align:start
[giggles]

00:48:30.036 --> 00:48:31.103 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Anna hiccups]

00:48:32.672 --> 00:48:33.973 position:30% line:89% align:start
Too much wine?

00:48:37.610 --> 00:48:39.212 position:35% line:89% align:start
Who was he?

00:48:39.246 --> 00:48:40.646 position:33% line:89% align:start
Who was who?

00:48:40.680 --> 00:48:41.847 position:7% line:89% align:start
The one I saw you dancing with.

00:48:43.083 --> 00:48:46.953 position:21% line:83% align:start
Ah! Kazuhiko? He's an
old friend of mine.

00:48:46.986 --> 00:48:50.890 position:21% line:83% align:start
Oh. He's a very good
dancer, isn't he.

00:48:50.923 --> 00:48:52.025 position:35% line:89% align:start
So are you.

00:48:56.063 --> 00:48:58.831 position:24% line:83% align:start
Well, in that case,
may I have this dance?

00:49:01.001 --> 00:49:02.235 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:49:03.103 --> 00:49:05.205 position:16% line:89% align:start
Wait, but, I can't dance.

00:49:05.238 --> 00:49:07.140 position:10% line:89% align:start
Don't worry, follow my lead.

00:49:08.075 --> 00:49:09.675 position:33% line:89% align:start
[stammering]

00:49:09.709 --> 00:49:19.252 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Marnie humming]

00:49:19.286 --> 00:49:22.289 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Marnie humming]

00:49:22.322 --> 00:49:28.729 position:21% line:89% align:start
♪ <i>La la la la la...</i> ♪

00:49:28.762 --> 00:49:35.035 position:21% line:89% align:start
♪ <i>do do do do do...</i> ♪

00:49:35.068 --> 00:49:42.142 position:21% line:89% align:start
♪ <i>la la la la la...</i> ♪

00:49:42.175 --> 00:49:44.911 position:27% line:89% align:start
[classical music]

00:49:44.945 --> 00:49:49.016 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

00:49:51.319 --> 00:49:58.925 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:50:04.198 --> 00:50:06.234 position:16% line:89% align:start
Look for me again, Anna.

00:50:07.934 --> 00:50:11.239 position:16% line:83% align:start
And don't tell anyone our
precious secret. You promise?

00:50:11.272 --> 00:50:12.306 position:41% line:89% align:start
Uh-huh.

00:50:12.974 --> 00:50:16.010 position:35% line:89% align:start
[giggling]

00:50:16.044 --> 00:50:18.079 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
Wait, wait...

00:50:18.112 --> 00:50:20.281 position:30% line:89% align:start
[both laughing]

00:50:20.314 --> 00:50:23.251 position:27% line:89% align:start
[peaceful music]

00:50:35.797 --> 00:50:36.898 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:50:36.931 --> 00:50:37.999 position:44% line:83% align:start
[man]
I thought I saw something.

00:50:43.871 --> 00:50:48.009 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's that girl, the one
staying with the Oiwas.

00:50:48.042 --> 00:50:50.678 position:27% line:89% align:start
[peaceful music]

00:51:03.358 --> 00:51:08.129 position:27% line:89% align:start
[birds chirping]

00:51:13.901 --> 00:51:15.903 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Setsu] <i>Waiting for the</i>
 <i>other shoe to drop...</i>

00:51:15.937 --> 00:51:19.006 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>If only the saying was waiting</i>
 <i>for the other shoe to show up!</i>

00:51:19.040 --> 00:51:21.343 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm sure it's somewhere.

00:51:21.376 --> 00:51:22.377 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'll look for it.

00:51:23.845 --> 00:51:25.947 position:27% line:83% align:start
You know how many
shoes I've lost out there?

00:51:25.981 --> 00:51:27.216 position:27% line:83% align:start
If you dig around
that marsh

00:51:27.249 --> 00:51:29.218 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'll bet you find a
few pairs of mine.

00:51:29.251 --> 00:51:31.853 position:10% line:89% align:start
And none of them in her size.

00:51:31.887 --> 00:51:35.023 position:10% line:83% align:start
Never mind. Our daughter left
some shoes in the attic.

00:51:35.057 --> 00:51:36.959 position:30% line:83% align:start
I'll bring them
out just in case.

00:51:36.992 --> 00:51:38.393 position:7% line:89% align:start
Thank you. That would be great.

00:51:41.430 --> 00:51:43.332 position:27% line:89% align:start
[birds chirping]

00:51:45.367 --> 00:51:46.702 position:33% line:89% align:start
There it is.

00:51:56.712 --> 00:51:57.946 position:41% line:89% align:start
Marnie.

00:52:32.915 --> 00:52:34.150 position:44% line:89% align:start
Wow.

00:52:36.186 --> 00:52:40.390 position:19% line:83% align:start
Not only are they big,
but my, oh my, are they tasty.

00:52:40.423 --> 00:52:41.890 position:44% line:89% align:start
Here.

00:52:41.924 --> 00:52:43.692 position:33% line:89% align:start
[stammering]

00:52:56.772 --> 00:52:59.209 position:21% line:83% align:start
You're quite talented
with a knife there.

00:52:59.242 --> 00:53:01.911 position:30% line:83% align:start
I like to cook.
Auntie teaches me all the time.

00:53:01.945 --> 00:53:04.414 position:19% line:83% align:start
Anna, you're so polite
and well-behaved.

00:53:04.447 --> 00:53:06.916 position:19% line:83% align:start
My daughter could learn
a thing or two from you.

00:53:10.320 --> 00:53:12.255 position:16% line:89% align:start
Careful, watch your back.

00:53:12.288 --> 00:53:13.856 position:30% line:83% align:start
You know, I can
remember when

00:53:13.890 --> 00:53:16.359 position:27% line:83% align:start
you first came to
Yoriko's place.

00:53:16.392 --> 00:53:19.295 position:10% line:89% align:start
You should've seen her face.

00:53:19.329 --> 00:53:23.266 position:24% line:83% align:start
My, oh my, that was
the happiest day of her life.

00:53:23.299 --> 00:53:26.102 position:19% line:89% align:start
Her only worry that day

00:53:26.135 --> 00:53:30.940 position:7% line:83% align:start
was how to make up for the five
years she hadn't had with you.

00:53:30.974 --> 00:53:33.076 position:13% line:83% align:start
That's probably where those
knife skills come from.

00:53:35.245 --> 00:53:37.348 position:27% line:83% align:start
She's always been
a worrier, that one.

00:53:38.582 --> 00:53:41.252 position:24% line:83% align:start
She would phone me
every other second.

00:53:41.285 --> 00:53:44.854 position:13% line:83% align:start
"Is Anna eating too little?
Is Anna eating too much?"

00:53:44.887 --> 00:53:47.291 position:13% line:83% align:start
Oh, sorry, I shouldn't tell
tales about your mother.

00:53:48.992 --> 00:53:50.527 position:19% line:89% align:start
I know what she's like.

00:53:50.561 --> 00:53:52.129 position:30% line:83% align:start
We have so many
pictures of you

00:53:52.162 --> 00:53:54.198 position:27% line:83% align:start
that Yoriko sent
us over the years.

00:53:54.231 --> 00:53:55.299 position:16% line:89% align:start
She's very proud of you.

00:53:56.300 --> 00:53:57.767 position:13% line:89% align:start
I'll show 'em to you later.

00:54:01.338 --> 00:54:03.407 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Kiyomasa Oiwa]
 <i>Aww, Setsu, look!</i>

00:54:03.440 --> 00:54:06.410 position:13% line:83% align:start
I just found the wind chime
I made on our honeymoon.

00:54:06.443 --> 00:54:07.844 position:35% line:89% align:start
[jingling]

00:54:07.878 --> 00:54:10.014 position:24% line:83% align:start
Little distraction
from the heat.

00:54:12.449 --> 00:54:15.319 position:30% line:83% align:start
Looks like your
hair's growing out.

00:54:15.352 --> 00:54:17.288 position:16% line:89% align:start
How 'bout a little trim?

00:54:17.321 --> 00:54:19.857 position:5% line:89% align:start
Right. That would be a disaster.

00:54:21.992 --> 00:54:23.193 position:21% line:89% align:start
[wind chime jingling]

00:54:47.284 --> 00:54:49.086 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>Marnie...?</i>

00:54:49.119 --> 00:54:50.622 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Marnie]
 <i>Look for me again.</i>

00:54:50.655 --> 00:54:52.357 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:54:56.594 --> 00:54:59.163 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:54:59.197 --> 00:55:01.131 position:16% line:83% align:start
I can't believe I almost
forgot about Marnie!

00:55:03.000 --> 00:55:06.338 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:55:10.275 --> 00:55:11.343 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:55:15.680 --> 00:55:16.981 position:38% line:89% align:start
Marnie...

00:55:20.185 --> 00:55:23.455 position:24% line:89% align:start
[thunder rumbling]

00:55:23.488 --> 00:55:24.522 position:41% line:89% align:start
Marnie!

00:55:30.228 --> 00:55:31.529 position:38% line:89% align:start
Marnie...

00:55:31.563 --> 00:55:34.399 position:24% line:89% align:start
[thunder rumbling]

00:55:37.435 --> 00:55:40.505 position:27% line:89% align:start
[rain spattering]

00:56:10.034 --> 00:56:11.370 position:30% line:89% align:start
Would you mind?

00:56:13.138 --> 00:56:14.005 position:41% line:89% align:start
Please.

00:56:15.039 --> 00:56:17.510 position:7% line:89% align:start
I see you're an artist as well.

00:56:17.543 --> 00:56:20.546 position:19% line:83% align:start
Your drawing looks like
someone I once knew.

00:56:20.579 --> 00:56:22.314 position:30% line:89% align:start
She was lovely.

00:56:24.150 --> 00:56:26.218 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
She is.

00:56:26.252 --> 00:56:28.920 position:33% line:83% align:start
But I haven't
seen her for a week.

00:56:31.290 --> 00:56:33.325 position:35% line:83% align:start
I wonder if
she's upset with me

00:56:33.359 --> 00:56:35.294 position:13% line:89% align:start
because I forgot about her.

00:56:36.462 --> 00:56:37.430 position:24% line:89% align:start
If she's a friend,

00:56:37.463 --> 00:56:40.032 position:24% line:83% align:start
everything will be
fine once you talk to her.

00:56:42.001 --> 00:56:44.270 position:33% line:83% align:start
Say, will you
please take a look?

00:56:44.303 --> 00:56:45.304 position:44% line:89% align:start
Sure.

00:56:51.377 --> 00:56:52.545 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:56:53.212 --> 00:56:54.046 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Anna] Wow.

00:56:54.079 --> 00:56:56.282 position:27% line:83% align:start
Do you think the
colors are too messy?

00:56:56.315 --> 00:56:59.018 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
No, it's wonderful.

00:56:59.051 --> 00:57:00.553 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm Hisako.

00:57:00.586 --> 00:57:04.256 position:16% line:83% align:start
And I'm in love with that
old Marsh House. And you?

00:57:05.692 --> 00:57:08.762 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'm Anna. And I love it, too.

00:57:08.795 --> 00:57:10.664 position:27% line:89% align:start
[peaceful music]

00:57:15.334 --> 00:57:19.038 position:5% line:83% align:start
You know, we're going to have to
be quick with our artwork.

00:57:19.071 --> 00:57:21.508 position:10% line:89% align:start
Before the new folks move in.

00:57:21.541 --> 00:57:23.743 position:21% line:83% align:start
The renovation work's
already under way.

00:57:23.777 --> 00:57:25.244 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:57:25.277 --> 00:57:28.180 position:24% line:89% align:start
[machines whirring]

00:57:28.214 --> 00:57:30.484 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>[woman] Thanks for your hard</i>
 <i>work. Please, have some tea.</i>

00:57:30.517 --> 00:57:33.118 position:44% line:83% align:start
[man]
Thanks, much appreciated.

00:57:33.152 --> 00:57:35.589 position:13% line:83% align:start
- Hey, let's take a break!
- Sounds good to me.

00:57:37.524 --> 00:57:39.226 position:33% line:89% align:start
[clattering]

00:57:40.092 --> 00:57:41.127 position:41% line:89% align:start
[bangs]

00:57:41.161 --> 00:57:42.162 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:57:43.797 --> 00:57:45.265 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:57:50.470 --> 00:57:52.639 position:21% line:89% align:start
Hey, are you Marnie?

00:57:58.144 --> 00:57:59.479 position:24% line:89% align:start
Come on... come on!

00:58:13.660 --> 00:58:16.664 position:19% line:83% align:start
Wow, I hardly recognize
it from this side.

00:58:16.697 --> 00:58:18.398 position:27% line:83% align:start
Probably because
of the new paint job.

00:58:18.431 --> 00:58:20.233 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's not finished yet.
Come on.

00:58:21.802 --> 00:58:23.303 position:35% line:89% align:start
Hiya guys.

00:58:23.336 --> 00:58:24.572 position:19% line:89% align:start
Hi there. How are you?

00:58:24.605 --> 00:58:26.607 position:27% line:83% align:start
Got a friend with
you today, huh?

00:58:28.308 --> 00:58:31.177 position:33% line:83% align:start
You can wear
any of those slippers.

00:58:31.211 --> 00:58:32.279 position:38% line:89% align:start
A guest?

00:58:32.312 --> 00:58:33.681 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yeah, a secret one.

00:58:33.714 --> 00:58:35.115 position:41% line:89% align:start
Secret?

00:58:35.148 --> 00:58:37.552 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hey! Never mind.

00:58:37.585 --> 00:58:39.286 position:10% line:89% align:start
Sorry, make yourself at home.

00:58:40.421 --> 00:58:42.122 position:21% line:89% align:start
Thank you very much.

00:58:43.824 --> 00:58:46.694 position:7% line:89% align:start
Yes, yes, it's a lovely place.

00:58:48.496 --> 00:58:50.731 position:19% line:83% align:start
Yes, we're right in the
middle of renovation work.

00:58:52.767 --> 00:58:54.535 position:19% line:89% align:start
Is this the same room?

00:58:54.569 --> 00:58:55.836 position:21% line:89% align:start
[girl clears throat]

00:58:57.838 --> 00:58:59.173 position:38% line:89% align:start
Upstairs.

00:59:00.708 --> 00:59:02.777 position:13% line:89% align:start
I'm sure you know the way.

00:59:07.181 --> 00:59:09.183 position:19% line:89% align:start
Okay, this is my room.

00:59:11.852 --> 00:59:13.220 position:38% line:89% align:start
So it is.

00:59:17.692 --> 00:59:18.759 position:41% line:89% align:start
And so?

00:59:19.794 --> 00:59:21.195 position:27% line:89% align:start
It's a cute room.

00:59:23.164 --> 00:59:25.600 position:19% line:83% align:start
I believe this used to
be your room, correct?

00:59:25.633 --> 00:59:26.567 position:44% line:89% align:start
What?

00:59:27.335 --> 00:59:28.804 position:27% line:89% align:start
Don't play games.

00:59:28.837 --> 00:59:31.205 position:30% line:89% align:start
You are Marnie.

00:59:31.238 --> 00:59:34.241 position:16% line:89% align:start
Marnie? Really, I'm not.

00:59:34.275 --> 00:59:35.811 position:33% line:83% align:start
What? So then
why do I see you

00:59:35.844 --> 00:59:37.578 position:27% line:83% align:start
looking up at my
window all the time?

00:59:37.613 --> 00:59:38.880 position:30% line:89% align:start
Because... I...

00:59:38.914 --> 00:59:42.316 position:16% line:83% align:start
C'mon. I'm going to show
you where I see you.

00:59:42.350 --> 00:59:44.620 position:7% line:89% align:start
See. You're always down there.

00:59:46.655 --> 00:59:48.289 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'm not Marnie.

00:59:48.322 --> 00:59:51.325 position:16% line:83% align:start
I just love this mansion,
I draw it all the time.

00:59:51.359 --> 00:59:52.461 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Sayaka]
That can't be!

00:59:53.695 --> 00:59:55.364 position:7% line:89% align:start
How come you acted so surprised

00:59:55.397 --> 00:59:57.231 position:33% line:83% align:start
when I called
you Marnie earlier?

00:59:57.264 --> 01:00:00.167 position:7% line:83% align:start
What I want to know is, how do
you even know that name?

01:00:04.806 --> 01:00:06.808 position:10% line:89% align:start
I found it behind the shelf.

01:00:08.677 --> 01:00:10.212 position:38% line:89% align:start
A diary?

01:00:10.245 --> 01:00:12.681 position:7% line:89% align:start
That's right. It's your diary.

01:00:18.920 --> 01:00:20.355 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:00:20.389 --> 01:00:21.690 position:41% line:89% align:start
Marnie!

01:00:23.692 --> 01:00:28.196 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'll go pour you some
Queen Mary, your favorite,

01:00:28.230 --> 01:00:29.531 position:19% line:89% align:start
and I'll be right back.

01:00:33.368 --> 01:00:35.804 position:27% line:89% align:start
[peaceful music]

01:00:35.838 --> 01:00:38.306 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Marnie] <i>"Last night I went</i>
 <i>for a row in my nightie.</i>

01:00:39.708 --> 01:00:40.943 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Marnie and Anna]
 <i>The marsh and the moon</i>

01:00:40.977 --> 01:00:42.577 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>were very pretty at night.</i>

01:00:44.346 --> 01:00:45.882 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Marnie]
 <i>I shall do it again.</i>

01:00:48.383 --> 01:00:50.953 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>June 8th. A party!</i>

01:00:52.320 --> 01:00:54.423 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>Father, Mother and many of</i>

01:00:54.456 --> 01:00:57.325 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>their friends came.</i>
 <i>It was such fun.</i>

01:00:58.995 --> 01:01:01.263 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>I went outside from the sunroom</i>

01:01:02.397 --> 01:01:05.200 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>and danced with a flower girl.</i>

01:01:07.269 --> 01:01:08.438 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>But...</i>

01:01:08.471 --> 01:01:11.239 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Nan locked me in my room</i>
 <i>because of last night.</i>

01:01:15.678 --> 01:01:18.881 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>So there won't be any midnight</i>
 <i>boat rides for a while."</i>

01:01:24.287 --> 01:01:25.588 position:33% line:89% align:start
[door opens]

01:01:26.622 --> 01:01:29.325 position:24% line:83% align:start
See, it's actually
you, isn't it?

01:01:31.494 --> 01:01:32.662 position:33% line:89% align:start
No, it's not.

01:01:33.596 --> 01:01:34.731 position:21% line:89% align:start
Marnie is someone...

01:01:35.531 --> 01:01:36.666 position:35% line:89% align:start
someone...

01:01:37.767 --> 01:01:40.636 position:24% line:83% align:start
She's just someone
that I invented.

01:01:42.371 --> 01:01:45.775 position:24% line:83% align:start
An imaginary girl,
only in my mind.

01:01:45.808 --> 01:01:46.709 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

01:01:46.743 --> 01:01:48.912 position:21% line:83% align:start
But I suppose this is
Marnie's diary.

01:01:50.646 --> 01:01:53.716 position:7% line:83% align:start
And I suppose it's as if she's
really lived here in this room.

01:01:55.551 --> 01:01:58.889 position:19% line:83% align:start
OK, no messing around.
You're really not her?

01:01:58.922 --> 01:01:59.957 position:47% line:89% align:start
No.

01:01:59.990 --> 01:02:02.325 position:21% line:89% align:start
She's only imaginary?

01:02:02.358 --> 01:02:03.359 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's right.

01:02:05.628 --> 01:02:07.898 position:19% line:83% align:start
But I thought you were,
and your diary said,

01:02:07.931 --> 01:02:11.334 position:13% line:89% align:start
and you came back.... ohhh.

01:02:13.503 --> 01:02:17.440 position:5% line:83% align:start
My name is Anna. And I came from
Sapporo for the summer.

01:02:17.473 --> 01:02:19.877 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hiya. I'm Sayaka.

01:02:19.910 --> 01:02:21.912 position:19% line:89% align:start
And I come from Tokyo.

01:02:22.980 --> 01:02:25.649 position:35% line:83% align:start
Wait a sec.
If she was imaginary,

01:02:25.682 --> 01:02:28.051 position:30% line:83% align:start
why is the name
in the diary the same?

01:02:29.386 --> 01:02:30.921 position:33% line:89% align:start
I don't know.

01:02:30.954 --> 01:02:36.460 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Sayaka] Marnie must be real.
I'm going to investigate again!

01:02:36.493 --> 01:02:40.764 position:27% line:89% align:start
[peaceful music]

01:02:48.872 --> 01:02:50.607 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>Marnie...</i>

01:02:53.710 --> 01:02:56.780 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>who... are you?</i>

01:03:04.855 --> 01:03:07.992 position:30% line:89% align:start
[wind rustling]

01:03:18.136 --> 01:03:19.403 position:35% line:89% align:start
Is that me?

01:03:19.436 --> 01:03:21.371 position:38% line:89% align:start
Huh? Oh!

01:03:27.679 --> 01:03:29.948 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's you... Marnie!

01:03:33.952 --> 01:03:36.521 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:03:41.993 --> 01:03:46.865 position:10% line:83% align:start
Wait, Marnie, no. That one...
it's not done!

01:03:46.898 --> 01:03:49.567 position:16% line:89% align:start
Wow! You are really good.

01:03:49.601 --> 01:03:51.436 position:30% line:89% align:start
Oh, thank you.

01:03:51.469 --> 01:03:56.007 position:10% line:83% align:start
I've never had anyone draw me
before. How nice! I love it!

01:04:04.616 --> 01:04:05.950 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
I missed you.

01:04:08.753 --> 01:04:11.389 position:21% line:83% align:start
I called for you and
in my heart I shouted.

01:04:15.560 --> 01:04:16.962 position:35% line:89% align:start
And I, you.

01:04:16.996 --> 01:04:18.463 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Marnie]
Come with me.

01:04:18.496 --> 01:04:19.564 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
No.

01:04:20.798 --> 01:04:23.668 position:16% line:89% align:start
You come with me, please.

01:04:26.504 --> 01:04:29.808 position:19% line:83% align:start
I- I can't go very far
from the mansion.

01:04:31.877 --> 01:04:36.081 position:10% line:83% align:start
Okay, then. We'll go wherever
it is that you want to go.

01:04:38.583 --> 01:04:42.888 position:27% line:89% align:start
[peaceful music]

01:05:05.844 --> 01:05:08.681 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Anna] <i>You sure know a lot</i>
 <i>about mushrooms, Marnie.</i>

01:05:08.714 --> 01:05:12.051 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Marnie] <i>Father taught</i>
 <i>me when I was little.</i>

01:05:12.084 --> 01:05:16.956 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>I once brought home</i>
 <i>three bags full of mushrooms.</i>

01:05:16.989 --> 01:05:19.625 position:19% line:83% align:start
You should've seen the
look on my mother's face.

01:05:19.658 --> 01:05:20.793 position:38% line:89% align:start
[giggles]

01:05:27.900 --> 01:05:30.903 position:33% line:83% align:start
Why so quiet?
Are you alright?

01:05:33.706 --> 01:05:35.976 position:16% line:89% align:start
Marnie, you are so lucky.

01:05:36.009 --> 01:05:39.012 position:5% line:89% align:start
I wish... I wish that I was you.

01:05:48.955 --> 01:05:50.090 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tell me.

01:05:53.226 --> 01:05:54.593 position:33% line:89% align:start
Well, I'm...

01:05:56.562 --> 01:05:57.931 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
I'm a foster child.

01:05:59.132 --> 01:06:02.002 position:21% line:83% align:start
My real parents died
when I was little.

01:06:02.035 --> 01:06:03.169 position:21% line:89% align:start
My grandmother, too.

01:06:04.337 --> 01:06:06.940 position:24% line:83% align:start
I know they didn't
die on purpose, but...

01:06:06.973 --> 01:06:08.575 position:21% line:89% align:start
sometimes I feel like

01:06:08.608 --> 01:06:09.843 position:19% line:89% align:start
I can't forgive them...

01:06:10.744 --> 01:06:12.779 position:16% line:89% align:start
for leaving me all alone.

01:06:22.922 --> 01:06:25.125 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'm actually jealous of you.

01:06:25.158 --> 01:06:27.994 position:19% line:83% align:start
I think you're lucky to
be a foster child.

01:06:28.028 --> 01:06:30.630 position:16% line:83% align:start
If you really didn't have
any relatives left

01:06:30.663 --> 01:06:33.200 position:19% line:83% align:start
then the folks who took
you in as a daughter

01:06:33.234 --> 01:06:35.869 position:33% line:83% align:start
must be truly
kindhearted people.

01:06:49.083 --> 01:06:51.785 position:27% line:83% align:start
So, shall I tell
you a big secret?

01:06:53.087 --> 01:06:54.955 position:33% line:83% align:start
It's about my
foster parents.

01:06:54.989 --> 01:07:00.161 position:10% line:83% align:start
It's complicated, and they're
really nice people, but...

01:07:00.194 --> 01:07:01.896 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm not their real child,

01:07:01.929 --> 01:07:04.597 position:24% line:83% align:start
yet they raised me,
which I appreciate.

01:07:07.034 --> 01:07:09.003 position:38% line:83% align:start
But once,
I saw some documents.

01:07:10.337 --> 01:07:13.941 position:13% line:83% align:start
Those documents showed that
my foster parents are...

01:07:13.974 --> 01:07:15.709 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>paid to look after me.</i>

01:07:15.743 --> 01:07:17.011 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Marnie]
 <i>Really?</i>

01:07:17.044 --> 01:07:19.713 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Anna] <i>Really. It was a</i>
 <i>letter from the government.</i>

01:07:21.248 --> 01:07:22.850 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>It said something</i>
 <i>about how they were</i>

01:07:22.883 --> 01:07:25.252 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>going to increase</i>
 <i>the subsidy for me.</i>

01:07:25.286 --> 01:07:28.022 position:24% line:89% align:start
[melancholic music]

01:07:28.055 --> 01:07:30.124 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Marnie] <i>But, I'm sure</i>
 <i>there was a reason...</i>

01:07:30.157 --> 01:07:32.026 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Anna] <i>I don't care what</i>
 <i>the reason is</i> !

01:07:33.794 --> 01:07:37.832 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>They wouldn't get that money</i>
 <i>if I were their real child.</i>

01:07:37.865 --> 01:07:40.067 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>It's because I'm not</i>
 <i>that they get paid.</i>

01:07:42.903 --> 01:07:46.006 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>Even worse...</i>
 <i>they hide it from me.</i>

01:07:52.247 --> 01:07:53.315 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

01:07:54.949 --> 01:07:55.983 position:5% line:89% align:start
I can see why that would hurt...

01:07:56.016 --> 01:07:59.121 position:13% line:83% align:start
but that doesn't mean that
Auntie doesn't love you.

01:07:59.154 --> 01:08:01.889 position:16% line:89% align:start
Seriously? Don't you see?

01:08:01.922 --> 01:08:06.027 position:10% line:83% align:start
None of the other kids in the
building get money! Only we do!

01:08:06.061 --> 01:08:08.396 position:30% line:83% align:start
And she always
has this worried look,

01:08:08.430 --> 01:08:11.699 position:19% line:83% align:start
as if I'm going to find
out about it, and then...

01:08:11.732 --> 01:08:16.138 position:27% line:83% align:start
I hate myself for
worrying about this, too.

01:08:16.171 --> 01:08:19.773 position:35% line:83% align:start
I can't...
I... I can't...

01:08:19.807 --> 01:08:21.877 position:10% line:89% align:start
believe in anything anymore.

01:08:21.910 --> 01:08:25.713 position:38% line:89% align:start
[crying]

01:08:31.086 --> 01:08:33.788 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's ok... it's ok to cry.

01:08:33.822 --> 01:08:36.691 position:30% line:83% align:start
Just know that
I love you, forever.

01:08:38.793 --> 01:08:41.429 position:21% line:83% align:start
I love you more than
any girl I've ever known.

01:08:45.901 --> 01:08:48.937 position:16% line:83% align:start
I think it's your turn to
tell me a secret next.

01:08:48.970 --> 01:08:49.771 position:44% line:89% align:start
Fine.

01:08:50.739 --> 01:08:52.475 position:27% line:83% align:start
It was only when
I was very young

01:08:52.508 --> 01:08:54.342 position:24% line:83% align:start
that I went picking
mushrooms with Father.

01:08:57.480 --> 01:09:00.682 position:19% line:83% align:start
Nowadays, I hardly see
Father or Mother.

01:09:02.318 --> 01:09:04.453 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Marnie] <i>Mother's usually</i>
 <i>away traveling</i> .

01:09:04.487 --> 01:09:05.887 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whooshing]

01:09:09.292 --> 01:09:10.859 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>And due to Father's work</i>

01:09:10.892 --> 01:09:14.263 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>he only comes home</i>
 <i>about twice a year.</i>

01:09:14.297 --> 01:09:16.365 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>So, the only ones at the</i>

01:09:16.399 --> 01:09:19.968 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>mansion are Nan, and</i>
 <i>the two maids...</i>

01:09:20.001 --> 01:09:21.237 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>and me.</i>

01:09:22.338 --> 01:09:25.774 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>I slip out while</i>
 <i>they're gossiping.</i>

01:09:25.807 --> 01:09:29.178 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>And look how free I get to be!</i>

01:09:29.212 --> 01:09:31.113 position:38% line:89% align:start
[humming]

01:09:32.847 --> 01:09:37.019 position:7% line:83% align:start
But it really is glorious when
Father and Mother are home.

01:09:37.053 --> 01:09:38.254 position:24% line:89% align:start
They host parties!

01:09:39.322 --> 01:09:42.325 position:27% line:83% align:start
Yeah... like the
one the other night.

01:09:42.358 --> 01:09:45.127 position:19% line:89% align:start
With my amazing parents

01:09:45.161 --> 01:09:49.432 position:21% line:83% align:start
and so many glamorous
delightful people!

01:09:49.465 --> 01:09:53.135 position:7% line:83% align:start
And I always get to have a new
dress and I always get to dance.

01:09:54.837 --> 01:09:56.939 position:33% line:83% align:start
That's when I
tell myself that I'm

01:09:56.973 --> 01:09:59.875 position:21% line:83% align:start
the luckiest girl in
the whole wide world.

01:10:01.277 --> 01:10:02.445 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

01:10:12.356 --> 01:10:17.361 position:13% line:83% align:start
Oh, Anna... will you be my
friend forever and ever?

01:10:19.161 --> 01:10:20.229 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yes, of course.

01:10:20.264 --> 01:10:21.465 position:27% line:89% align:start
Forever and ever.

01:10:21.498 --> 01:10:22.865 position:24% line:83% align:start
- [girls giggling]
- Huh?

01:10:27.504 --> 01:10:30.340 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Marnie]
 <i>Nan's always in a foul mood.</i>

01:10:30.374 --> 01:10:35.579 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>She yanks me by the arm,</i>
 <i>brushes my hair very hard...</i>

01:10:35.612 --> 01:10:38.382 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>No would imagine</i>
 <i>I'm being bullied, right?</i>

01:10:38.415 --> 01:10:40.850 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>But it really hurts.</i>

01:10:40.883 --> 01:10:42.219 position:30% line:89% align:start
Enough to cry.

01:10:43.387 --> 01:10:45.989 position:7% line:89% align:start
The maids love to frighten me.

01:10:46.023 --> 01:10:49.059 position:13% line:83% align:start
When I was small, they used
to threaten me, saying

01:10:49.092 --> 01:10:51.395 position:27% line:83% align:start
"Naughty children
get shut in the silo

01:10:51.428 --> 01:10:53.563 position:21% line:83% align:start
where ghosts suck out
their souls."

01:10:59.102 --> 01:11:02.005 position:30% line:83% align:start
Do you mean the
silo on the hill?

01:11:02.039 --> 01:11:03.840 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yes, and once...

01:11:03.874 --> 01:11:06.243 position:19% line:83% align:start
on a stormy night they
dragged me up there.

01:11:06.276 --> 01:11:07.411 position:38% line:89% align:start
[crying]

01:11:07.444 --> 01:11:10.580 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>All the way up I was</i>
 <i>kicking and screaming.</i>

01:11:10.615 --> 01:11:13.350 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>I was so frightened</i>
 <i>I thought I'd die.</i>

01:11:13.383 --> 01:11:15.919 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>Then, just as we got there,</i>

01:11:15.952 --> 01:11:18.355 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>as the sky turned its darkest-</i>

01:11:18.388 --> 01:11:20.023 position:24% line:89% align:start
[lightning crashes]

01:11:20.057 --> 01:11:20.857 position:44% line:83% align:start
[all]
Ahhh!

01:11:22.125 --> 01:11:25.228 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>The maids were terrified,</i>
 <i>so we didn't go inside.</i>

01:11:26.631 --> 01:11:30.901 position:24% line:83% align:start
Anna, I think I can
endure anything else...

01:11:30.934 --> 01:11:33.304 position:19% line:89% align:start
anything but the silo.

01:11:34.472 --> 01:11:37.508 position:19% line:83% align:start
I have never heard such
a terrible thing!

01:11:37.542 --> 01:11:40.844 position:16% line:83% align:start
I hope the maids and Nan
do get struck by lightning!

01:11:42.112 --> 01:11:43.146 position:35% line:89% align:start
Never mind.

01:11:43.181 --> 01:11:47.352 position:13% line:83% align:start
Hasn't anyone ever tried to
frighten you before?

01:11:47.385 --> 01:11:50.254 position:19% line:83% align:start
No way! And definitely
not on purpose.

01:11:52.022 --> 01:11:54.325 position:5% line:89% align:start
Well, that was my little secret.

01:11:54.359 --> 01:11:56.260 position:24% line:89% align:start
Anna, you're lucky.

01:11:56.294 --> 01:11:57.395 position:27% line:89% align:start
I wish I was you.

01:11:57.428 --> 01:11:59.597 position:24% line:83% align:start
- [water splashes]
- [Marnie gasps]

01:11:59.630 --> 01:12:01.265 position:33% line:89% align:start
Our castle...

01:12:04.335 --> 01:12:07.372 position:10% line:83% align:start
Please don't worry about it.
Oh Marnie...

01:12:07.405 --> 01:12:09.574 position:16% line:89% align:start
I love you so very much.

01:12:09.607 --> 01:12:11.876 position:10% line:89% align:start
More than anyone I've known.

01:12:13.945 --> 01:12:15.146 position:30% line:89% align:start
Makes me happy.

01:12:16.514 --> 01:12:20.985 position:27% line:89% align:start
[peaceful music]

01:12:21.018 --> 01:12:25.423 position:16% line:83% align:start
Funny, it's kind of like
we traded places.

01:12:25.456 --> 01:12:27.024 position:38% line:89% align:start
How true.

01:12:27.458 --> 01:12:33.599 position:33% line:89% align:start
[both laugh]

01:12:33.632 --> 01:12:36.000 position:10% line:89% align:start
Oh no. The tide's coming in.

01:12:37.335 --> 01:12:40.138 position:27% line:83% align:start
Hey, let's go to
the silo together.

01:12:40.171 --> 01:12:41.172 position:44% line:89% align:start
What?

01:12:41.205 --> 01:12:43.941 position:21% line:83% align:start
The stories about the
ghosts can't be true.

01:12:43.975 --> 01:12:45.143 position:24% line:89% align:start
We'll go make sure.

01:12:46.412 --> 01:12:49.581 position:10% line:89% align:start
Tomorrow... no, let's go now!

01:12:57.222 --> 01:12:59.491 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Anna] <i>I don't care</i>
 <i>who Marnie really is.</i>

01:13:00.692 --> 01:13:02.594 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>I just want to help her.</i>

01:13:08.767 --> 01:13:14.106 position:30% line:89% align:start
[wind rushing]

01:13:15.607 --> 01:13:16.608 position:21% line:89% align:start
Are you okay, Marnie?

01:13:18.243 --> 01:13:22.214 position:13% line:83% align:start
Yes, I'm okay. I'll be fine
as long as I'm with you.

01:13:22.247 --> 01:13:23.549 position:38% line:89% align:start
Kazuhiko.

01:13:23.582 --> 01:13:25.451 position:35% line:89% align:start
Huh? I, um-

01:13:33.292 --> 01:13:35.127 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Sayaka]
 <i>Anna!</i>

01:13:35.795 --> 01:13:39.331 position:13% line:89% align:start
Anna! Hey! Perfect timing!

01:13:40.599 --> 01:13:42.000 position:35% line:89% align:start
I found it!

01:13:42.034 --> 01:13:43.035 position:44% line:89% align:start
Anna!

01:13:44.303 --> 01:13:47.105 position:27% line:89% align:start
[thunder rumbles]

01:13:48.808 --> 01:13:52.478 position:19% line:83% align:start
Look at this, only the
rest of the diary!

01:13:52.512 --> 01:13:54.112 position:38% line:89% align:start
Marnie...

01:13:55.414 --> 01:13:58.418 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry. Another time.

01:13:58.451 --> 01:14:01.387 position:30% line:83% align:start
Aww! But it's a
major discovery...

01:14:02.555 --> 01:14:04.757 position:19% line:89% align:start
And it's going to rain!

01:14:06.091 --> 01:14:09.027 position:30% line:89% align:start
[wind blowing]

01:14:14.400 --> 01:14:16.302 position:30% line:89% align:start
[bats chirping]

01:14:16.336 --> 01:14:18.404 position:24% line:89% align:start
[thunder rumbling]

01:14:22.509 --> 01:14:25.678 position:27% line:89% align:start
[rain pattering]

01:14:31.818 --> 01:14:36.089 position:27% line:89% align:start
[water dripping]

01:14:44.731 --> 01:14:46.733 position:30% line:83% align:start
- [whimpering]
- [Anna gasps]

01:14:49.102 --> 01:14:52.438 position:35% line:89% align:start
[squeaking]

01:14:52.472 --> 01:14:53.573 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Anna gasps]

01:14:53.606 --> 01:14:54.708 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ahh!

01:14:56.643 --> 01:14:59.612 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

01:14:59.647 --> 01:15:00.648 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Marnie]
 <i>Who is it?</i>

01:15:02.515 --> 01:15:04.284 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>Is someone there?</i>

01:15:04.317 --> 01:15:05.586 position:41% line:89% align:start
Marnie!

01:15:09.723 --> 01:15:13.460 position:21% line:83% align:start
So you did go ahead.
Don't scare me like that.

01:15:16.229 --> 01:15:17.263 position:41% line:89% align:start
Marnie!

01:15:21.535 --> 01:15:23.571 position:13% line:89% align:start
Are you okay? Why did you-

01:15:23.604 --> 01:15:24.605 position:38% line:89% align:start
Kazuhiko!

01:15:25.739 --> 01:15:29.843 position:30% line:83% align:start
I'm frightened!
I heard someone below.

01:15:29.877 --> 01:15:33.847 position:5% line:83% align:start
Oh, I thought I'd die of fright.
Kazuhiko...

01:15:33.881 --> 01:15:38.352 position:13% line:83% align:start
What are you talking about?
It's me, Anna! What's going on?

01:15:38.385 --> 01:15:40.187 position:33% line:89% align:start
Anna... Anna!

01:15:41.288 --> 01:15:43.791 position:24% line:83% align:start
I don't want anyone
making fun of me!

01:15:43.824 --> 01:15:45.593 position:10% line:89% align:start
But I haven't the courage...

01:15:45.626 --> 01:15:46.760 position:35% line:89% align:start
Oh, Anna...

01:15:48.162 --> 01:15:50.764 position:27% line:83% align:start
You have courage.
Look, you came up here.

01:15:53.233 --> 01:15:54.234 position:30% line:89% align:start
Let's go home.

01:15:55.904 --> 01:16:02.409 position:35% line:83% align:start
- [moaning]
- [Marnie whimpering]

01:16:02.443 --> 01:16:05.145 position:27% line:89% align:start
[rain pattering]

01:16:08.515 --> 01:16:09.450 position:44% line:89% align:start
Wait!

01:16:13.520 --> 01:16:15.690 position:10% line:89% align:start
It's only the wind. Let's go!

01:16:16.791 --> 01:16:18.660 position:35% line:83% align:start
You and me.
We'll go home together.

01:16:21.596 --> 01:16:22.831 position:35% line:89% align:start
[sniffles]

01:16:29.269 --> 01:16:32.774 position:30% line:89% align:start
[wind moaning]

01:16:32.807 --> 01:16:35.275 position:33% line:89% align:start
I... I can't!

01:16:35.309 --> 01:16:37.912 position:24% line:89% align:start
[thunder rumbling]

01:16:37.946 --> 01:16:40.382 position:21% line:89% align:start
Anna, come back here!

01:16:40.415 --> 01:16:41.716 position:30% line:89% align:start
Please... Anna!

01:16:41.750 --> 01:16:43.852 position:27% line:83% align:start
Hey, everything's
gonna be fine.

01:16:43.885 --> 01:16:46.488 position:30% line:83% align:start
I'm sure we'll
make it down.

01:16:46.521 --> 01:16:48.823 position:24% line:83% align:start
After all, we made
it up. Follow me.

01:16:50.825 --> 01:16:53.728 position:27% line:83% align:start
No! Please don't
leave me. Please!

01:16:53.762 --> 01:16:55.930 position:21% line:89% align:start
[lightning crackling]

01:16:55.964 --> 01:16:57.599 position:30% line:89% align:start
[rain pouring]

01:16:57.632 --> 01:17:02.337 position:30% line:83% align:start
[wind moaning,
thunder rumbling]

01:17:02.370 --> 01:17:03.638 position:24% line:89% align:start
[lightning cracks]

01:17:03.672 --> 01:17:04.773 position:47% line:89% align:start
No!

01:17:04.806 --> 01:17:06.941 position:30% line:89% align:start
[water rushing]

01:17:06.976 --> 01:17:08.243 position:41% line:89% align:start
Marnie!

01:17:09.244 --> 01:17:10.912 position:5% line:89% align:start
Let's go over there, it's safer.

01:17:25.293 --> 01:17:28.229 position:13% line:89% align:start
I'm cold... I'm so cold...

01:17:31.967 --> 01:17:36.438 position:21% line:83% align:start
Oh Anna, I'm scared.
It's horrible.

01:17:36.471 --> 01:17:39.842 position:7% line:83% align:start
Don't you worry, we'll be fine
as long as we're together.

01:17:39.875 --> 01:17:43.411 position:21% line:83% align:start
You did well, Marnie.
Real well.

01:17:43.445 --> 01:17:45.681 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Marnie crying]

01:17:46.482 --> 01:17:47.917 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:17:58.728 --> 01:18:05.668 position:38% line:89% align:start
[humming]

01:18:05.701 --> 01:18:14.477 position:35% line:89% align:start
[humming]

01:18:14.510 --> 01:18:20.983 position:7% line:83% align:start
- [woman] ♪ <i>La la la la la...</i> ♪
- [Marnie crying]

01:18:24.787 --> 01:18:26.255 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's fine. I'm here.

01:18:27.389 --> 01:18:28.624 position:38% line:89% align:start
Kazuhiko!

01:18:28.657 --> 01:18:30.559 position:13% line:89% align:start
I thought you'd never come.

01:18:32.661 --> 01:18:34.797 position:16% line:89% align:start
I thought you'd never...

01:18:35.631 --> 01:18:41.805 position:24% line:89% align:start
[continued humming]

01:18:42.873 --> 01:18:45.274 position:21% line:83% align:start
There, c'mon Marnie.
Let's go home.

01:18:46.375 --> 01:18:53.650 position:24% line:89% align:start
[continued humming]

01:18:57.721 --> 01:19:00.356 position:27% line:89% align:start
[rain pattering]

01:19:03.493 --> 01:19:05.562 position:30% line:89% align:start
[wind moaning]

01:19:05.595 --> 01:19:09.065 position:30% line:89% align:start
[water rushing]

01:19:09.099 --> 01:19:10.467 position:41% line:89% align:start
Marnie?

01:19:12.936 --> 01:19:14.604 position:41% line:89% align:start
Marnie?

01:19:15.672 --> 01:19:17.541 position:41% line:89% align:start
Marnie!

01:19:17.574 --> 01:19:21.812 position:30% line:83% align:start
[rain pouring,
wind rushing]

01:19:21.845 --> 01:19:24.381 position:41% line:89% align:start
Marnie!

01:19:24.915 --> 01:19:27.684 position:24% line:89% align:start
[thunder rumbling]

01:19:27.717 --> 01:19:31.488 position:24% line:89% align:start
[melancholic music]

01:19:31.521 --> 01:19:34.791 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>Marnie... you left me behind!</i>

01:19:42.599 --> 01:19:43.968 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Even you!</i>

01:19:44.001 --> 01:19:45.702 position:21% line:89% align:start
[lightning crackling]

01:19:47.972 --> 01:19:49.639 position:24% line:89% align:start
[thunder rumbling]

01:19:56.147 --> 01:19:58.381 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Anna grunts]

01:20:10.094 --> 01:20:13.130 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Sayaka]
Kazuhiko... Kazuhiko...

01:20:13.164 --> 01:20:15.900 position:5% line:89% align:start
This guy is all over this diary.

01:20:17.668 --> 01:20:22.707 position:19% line:83% align:start
"Kazuhiko is trying to
take me to the silo."

01:20:22.740 --> 01:20:23.474 position:41% line:89% align:start
Silo...

01:20:24.542 --> 01:20:26.477 position:21% line:83% align:start
- [knocking on door]
- [Sayaka gasps]

01:20:26.510 --> 01:20:27.678 position:41% line:89% align:start
What?!

01:20:28.913 --> 01:20:31.616 position:27% line:83% align:start
Easy! Why are you
so jumpy tonight?

01:20:31.649 --> 01:20:33.084 position:5% line:89% align:start
It's just supper time, Sherlock.

01:20:33.117 --> 01:20:34.185 position:30% line:89% align:start
Takeshi, wait!

01:20:34.218 --> 01:20:36.020 position:27% line:89% align:start
[rain pattering]

01:20:36.053 --> 01:20:39.423 position:21% line:83% align:start
I cannot believe you
talked me into this.

01:20:39.457 --> 01:20:40.359 position:27% line:89% align:start
It's not safe...

01:20:40.391 --> 01:20:43.694 position:27% line:83% align:start
And do you think
it's safe for my friend?!

01:20:43.728 --> 01:20:46.864 position:35% line:83% align:start
What if she
gets pneumonia? Oh!

01:20:49.734 --> 01:20:51.469 position:19% line:83% align:start
- [Takeshi] Is that...
- [Sayaka] Anna!

01:20:53.205 --> 01:20:54.672 position:24% line:89% align:start
Anna! Are you okay?

01:20:58.709 --> 01:20:59.944 position:35% line:89% align:start
So cruel...

01:20:59.978 --> 01:21:01.113 position:44% line:89% align:start
Anna?

01:21:01.146 --> 01:21:02.147 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Anna gasps]

01:21:03.048 --> 01:21:05.650 position:24% line:89% align:start
So cruel, Marnie...

01:21:05.683 --> 01:21:07.185 position:21% line:89% align:start
Oh, she's burning up!

01:21:07.219 --> 01:21:08.686 position:19% line:89% align:start
I'll go get some help.

01:21:09.821 --> 01:21:11.089 position:30% line:89% align:start
You'll be fine.

01:21:14.092 --> 01:21:15.961 position:27% line:83% align:start
- Hang in there.
- Be right back.

01:21:17.495 --> 01:21:18.830 position:41% line:89% align:start
Anna...

01:21:20.531 --> 01:21:24.002 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

01:21:24.970 --> 01:21:27.039 position:21% line:89% align:start
How is she doing now?

01:21:27.072 --> 01:21:29.641 position:30% line:83% align:start
Well, her fever
hasn't come down yet.

01:21:31.209 --> 01:21:33.679 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Setsu] <i>The doctor gave</i>
 <i>her a shot earlier, but...</i>

01:21:35.747 --> 01:21:37.082 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Sayaka]
 <i>I see.</i>

01:21:41.553 --> 01:21:44.122 position:33% line:89% align:start
[soft music]

01:21:48.260 --> 01:21:49.594 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>So cruel...</i>

01:21:51.997 --> 01:21:54.599 position:19% line:89% align:start
Marnie, how could you?

01:22:01.807 --> 01:22:03.675 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>I won't forgive you.</i>

01:22:03.709 --> 01:22:05.877 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Leaving me behind</i>
 <i>without a word.</i>

01:22:06.979 --> 01:22:09.614 position:30% line:89% align:start
[wind rushing]

01:22:12.985 --> 01:22:18.291 position:24% line:89% align:start
[melancholic music]

01:22:18.324 --> 01:22:20.994 position:24% line:89% align:start
[windows rattling]

01:22:25.164 --> 01:22:27.766 position:38% line:89% align:start
[banging]

01:22:29.701 --> 01:22:32.772 position:24% line:89% align:start
Anna! My dear Anna!

01:22:34.573 --> 01:22:38.643 position:21% line:83% align:start
Marnie! How could you
leave me behind back there?

01:22:38.678 --> 01:22:41.748 position:21% line:83% align:start
How could you betray
me like that!?

01:22:41.781 --> 01:22:44.951 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry, I didn't mean
to leave you all alone.

01:22:47.020 --> 01:22:49.055 position:21% line:89% align:start
But at that moment...

01:22:49.088 --> 01:22:51.224 position:16% line:89% align:start
You simply weren't there.

01:22:53.860 --> 01:22:55.895 position:13% line:89% align:start
What are you talking about?

01:22:55.928 --> 01:22:58.898 position:21% line:89% align:start
Oh, Anna, forgive me.

01:22:58.931 --> 01:23:02.168 position:24% line:83% align:start
Anna, I cannot stay
here any longer.

01:23:02.201 --> 01:23:04.704 position:10% line:89% align:start
I have to say goodbye to you.

01:23:06.205 --> 01:23:11.010 position:19% line:83% align:start
So please, Anna, I need
to hear that you forgive me.

01:23:11.044 --> 01:23:13.880 position:13% line:89% align:start
Please forgive me. Please.

01:23:14.947 --> 01:23:16.216 position:41% line:89% align:start
Anna...

01:23:19.219 --> 01:23:22.055 position:35% line:83% align:start
Of course,
I forgive you, Marnie!

01:23:22.088 --> 01:23:24.924 position:19% line:89% align:start
I love you. I love you!

01:23:24.957 --> 01:23:27.693 position:10% line:89% align:start
And I won't ever forget you!

01:23:27.727 --> 01:23:30.596 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'll never forget you! Ever!

01:23:30.630 --> 01:23:32.299 position:30% line:89% align:start
[wind rushing]

01:23:33.633 --> 01:23:37.703 position:24% line:83% align:start
- [waves crashing]
- [Anna whimpering]

01:23:51.651 --> 01:23:56.622 position:27% line:89% align:start
[peaceful music]

01:24:08.735 --> 01:24:09.937 position:24% line:89% align:start
[knocking on door]

01:24:12.239 --> 01:24:13.273 position:30% line:89% align:start
Feeling better?

01:24:14.442 --> 01:24:15.809 position:44% line:89% align:start
Anna?

01:24:20.114 --> 01:24:22.015 position:13% line:89% align:start
Sayaka has come to see you.

01:24:25.453 --> 01:24:26.653 position:41% line:89% align:start
Thanks.

01:24:30.057 --> 01:24:32.759 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Setsu] <i>Oh, you don't want</i>
 <i>to see her in your room?</i>

01:24:32.793 --> 01:24:35.028 position:19% line:5% align:start
[Anna] <i>No, I'll go out.</i>
 <i>It feels nice outside.</i>

01:24:38.266 --> 01:24:39.700 position:35% line:89% align:start
Hi Sayaka.

01:24:40.435 --> 01:24:42.303 position:13% line:89% align:start
Glad you're feeling better.

01:24:42.337 --> 01:24:43.837 position:27% line:89% align:start
Thanks very much!

01:24:43.871 --> 01:24:44.905 position:30% line:89% align:start
Something else.

01:24:47.708 --> 01:24:51.812 position:10% line:83% align:start
Reading this is what made me
think you might be at the silo.

01:24:51.845 --> 01:24:52.947 position:35% line:89% align:start
What is it?

01:24:52.981 --> 01:24:57.185 position:16% line:83% align:start
Remember the diary? Well,
those are the missing pages.

01:24:57.218 --> 01:25:00.421 position:21% line:83% align:start
You know, some things
I remember, some I don't.

01:25:00.455 --> 01:25:02.723 position:24% line:83% align:start
Well, I think this
might help you.

01:25:02.756 --> 01:25:07.829 position:7% line:83% align:start
I found a clue in this painting
that was behind the bookshelf.

01:25:07.862 --> 01:25:09.430 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Sayaka]
Maybe I'm psychic.

01:25:10.798 --> 01:25:12.200 position:33% line:89% align:start
Turn it over.

01:25:18.439 --> 01:25:20.141 position:38% line:83% align:start
- Hisako?
- Huh?

01:25:23.011 --> 01:25:24.812 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>Hisako!</i>

01:25:39.827 --> 01:25:41.796 position:21% line:83% align:start
Can you tell us what
you know about her?

01:25:41.829 --> 01:25:43.698 position:33% line:83% align:start
It would mean
a lot to me.

01:25:44.400 --> 01:25:45.967 position:33% line:89% align:start
Of course...

01:25:46.000 --> 01:25:48.470 position:21% line:83% align:start
but I'm afraid it's a
rather sad story.

01:25:48.504 --> 01:25:50.104 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm ready for it.

01:25:54.809 --> 01:25:57.712 position:10% line:89% align:start
It was a very long time ago.

01:25:59.281 --> 01:26:03.052 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Hisako] <i>I used to go play</i>
 <i>at the Marsh House quite often.</i>

01:26:03.085 --> 01:26:05.054 position:24% line:89% align:start
[melancholic music]

01:26:05.087 --> 01:26:07.389 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Marnie and I were</i>
 <i>still very little.</i>

01:26:07.423 --> 01:26:08.823 position:21% line:89% align:start
Oh wow, it's a bear!

01:26:08.856 --> 01:26:10.459 position:19% line:89% align:start
Let me see! Let me see.

01:26:10.492 --> 01:26:14.463 position:30% line:83% align:start
And look here.
This is my dashing dad!

01:26:14.496 --> 01:26:16.398 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Hisako]
 <i>Marnie loved to boast about</i>

01:26:16.432 --> 01:26:20.402 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>her glamorous parents and</i>
 <i>their extravagant parties.</i>

01:26:20.436 --> 01:26:22.871 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

01:26:25.241 --> 01:26:28.410 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>But the truth is,</i>
 <i>she was being neglected.</i>

01:26:31.113 --> 01:26:33.048 position:27% line:89% align:start
Goodbye, Marnie.

01:26:35.117 --> 01:26:37.019 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>That poor child...</i>

01:26:37.052 --> 01:26:39.488 position:21% line:89% align:start
Mama. Don't leave me!

01:26:39.521 --> 01:26:43.259 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Seems even the maids</i>
 <i>were bullying her.</i>

01:26:43.292 --> 01:26:44.760 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's awful!

01:26:46.295 --> 01:26:48.864 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Hisako]
 <i>Later, Marnie moved to Sapporo</i>

01:26:48.897 --> 01:26:52.101 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>and married Kazuhiko,</i>
 <i>her childhood friend.</i>

01:26:54.336 --> 01:26:57.507 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>With her family torn apart</i>
 <i>and feeling lost,</i>

01:26:57.540 --> 01:27:00.876 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>it was Kazuhiko who was</i>
 <i>always there to support her.</i>

01:27:02.845 --> 01:27:06.949 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Sayaka] <i>How romantic.</i>
 <i>So Kazuhiko was a good man!</i>

01:27:09.151 --> 01:27:12.322 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Hisako] <i>Two years later,</i>
 <i>Emily was born</i> .

01:27:12.355 --> 01:27:16.126 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Living at last in the warm</i>
 <i>household she'd always wanted,</i>

01:27:16.159 --> 01:27:18.428 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>Marnie was happy.</i>

01:27:21.097 --> 01:27:24.167 position:21% line:83% align:start
I didn't see her for
quite a while after that.

01:27:24.200 --> 01:27:26.869 position:7% line:89% align:start
The next time I saw her was...

01:27:26.902 --> 01:27:30.974 position:13% line:83% align:start
a few years after Kazuhiko
had died of an illness.

01:27:34.144 --> 01:27:35.612 position:19% line:89% align:start
Marnie was distraught.

01:27:35.645 --> 01:27:38.882 position:13% line:83% align:start
The shock of her husband's
death left her too ill

01:27:38.915 --> 01:27:41.951 position:35% line:83% align:start
and she was
placed in a sanatorium.

01:27:41.985 --> 01:27:43.219 position:35% line:89% align:start
Sanatorium?

01:27:44.354 --> 01:27:46.356 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's a place where you
go to get better.

01:27:47.624 --> 01:27:49.959 position:27% line:83% align:start
That is dreadful.
What happened to Emily?

01:27:51.328 --> 01:27:54.230 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Hisako] Marnie's
parents had passed away,

01:27:54.264 --> 01:27:57.400 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>leaving no one to</i>
 <i>look after her.</i>

01:27:57.434 --> 01:28:00.604 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Unable to cope, Marnie</i>
 <i>felt she had no choice</i>

01:28:00.638 --> 01:28:04.107 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>but to send young Emily</i>
 <i>off to boarding school.</i>

01:28:11.549 --> 01:28:14.250 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>By the time Emily</i>
 <i>returned at age 13,</i>

01:28:14.284 --> 01:28:16.986 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>she'd become a</i>
 <i>different child, they said.</i>

01:28:17.020 --> 01:28:18.188 position:41% line:89% align:start
Emily!

01:28:18.221 --> 01:28:20.890 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Hisako] <i>She was willful</i>
 <i>and independent</i> .

01:28:20.924 --> 01:28:23.294 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>And even though she knew</i>
 <i>her mother had been ill,</i>

01:28:23.327 --> 01:28:25.061 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>Emily bore a grudge</i>

01:28:25.095 --> 01:28:27.864 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>for being sent away at</i>
 <i>such an early age.</i>

01:28:29.266 --> 01:28:32.370 position:16% line:83% align:start
Oh, so now you're trying
to sound like a mother?

01:28:32.403 --> 01:28:34.938 position:21% line:83% align:start
I am your mother and
I'm simply saying

01:28:34.971 --> 01:28:37.907 position:27% line:83% align:start
you may not know
what's best for you.

01:28:37.941 --> 01:28:40.144 position:19% line:83% align:start
Are you even listening
to me at all?

01:28:40.177 --> 01:28:42.213 position:21% line:89% align:start
[arguing overlapping]

01:28:42.246 --> 01:28:44.315 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Hisako] <i>They never</i>
 <i>did make up after that.</i>

01:28:44.348 --> 01:28:46.350 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Marnie]
Emily, please. I'm your mother!

01:28:46.384 --> 01:28:47.618 position:30% line:83% align:start
I never thought
of you as a mother,

01:28:47.651 --> 01:28:49.420 position:13% line:89% align:start
even when you were around.

01:28:49.453 --> 01:28:53.324 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Hisako] <i>Emily ran away from</i>
 <i>home and soon got married.</i>

01:28:58.095 --> 01:29:00.164 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>She was expecting, you see.</i>

01:29:01.098 --> 01:29:03.134 position:27% line:83% align:start
- [phone ringing]
- [gasps]

01:29:06.103 --> 01:29:07.238 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>But then...</i>

01:29:17.716 --> 01:29:22.219 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>One night, Emily and her</i>
 <i>husband died in a car accident.</i>

01:29:25.356 --> 01:29:26.558 position:24% line:89% align:start
[melancholic music]

01:29:26.591 --> 01:29:29.093 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>I heard that Marnie</i>
 <i>took their little girl in.</i>

01:29:31.496 --> 01:29:36.133 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>She was determined to never</i>
 <i>let this child be lonely.</i>

01:29:38.236 --> 01:29:39.504 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>Still...</i>

01:29:39.538 --> 01:29:42.374 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>she couldn't get over</i>
 <i>the shock of losing Emily.</i>

01:29:44.709 --> 01:29:49.079 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Marnie became very ill,</i>
 <i>and died the next year.</i>

01:29:50.415 --> 01:29:53.418 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>That was about ten years ago.</i>

01:29:55.353 --> 01:29:57.489 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Sayaka crying]

01:29:58.523 --> 01:30:01.493 position:35% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry,
it's such a sad story.

01:30:02.661 --> 01:30:05.363 position:35% line:83% align:start
It's fine.
I really do appreciate it.

01:30:06.765 --> 01:30:09.534 position:13% line:89% align:start
Marnie adored that mansion.

01:30:12.604 --> 01:30:15.741 position:16% line:83% align:start
She loved the view of the
marsh from her window.

01:30:17.676 --> 01:30:21.546 position:16% line:83% align:start
She said it felt like the
birds were speaking to her.

01:30:23.515 --> 01:30:26.017 position:19% line:89% align:start
She had a lonely life,

01:30:26.051 --> 01:30:29.387 position:21% line:83% align:start
but she always lived
it to the fullest.

01:30:29.421 --> 01:30:33.458 position:10% line:83% align:start
She lived life with a smile,
determined to be happy.

01:30:35.661 --> 01:30:37.730 position:33% line:83% align:start
So you've met
Marnie too, then?

01:30:48.240 --> 01:30:49.509 position:24% line:89% align:start
[door hisses open]

01:30:49.542 --> 01:30:51.611 position:27% line:89% align:start
[engine rumbling]

01:30:58.651 --> 01:31:01.654 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Sayaka] <i>I really wish we</i>
 <i>could've played more.</i>

01:31:01.687 --> 01:31:03.189 position:30% line:83% align:start
I know, but the
plan was always

01:31:03.222 --> 01:31:05.558 position:24% line:83% align:start
for me to stay just
for the summer.

01:31:05.591 --> 01:31:08.094 position:19% line:83% align:start
Will you be here again
next summer?

01:31:08.127 --> 01:31:10.696 position:24% line:83% align:start
Certainly hope so.
We should keep in touch.

01:31:10.730 --> 01:31:13.432 position:19% line:89% align:start
Totally. Pinky promise?

01:31:14.367 --> 01:31:15.468 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
Pinky promise.

01:31:17.570 --> 01:31:21.374 position:5% line:83% align:start
Anna, I put the painting and the
diary back where I found them.

01:31:21.407 --> 01:31:24.143 position:16% line:89% align:start
Good, it's for the best.

01:31:24.176 --> 01:31:26.646 position:30% line:83% align:start
I haven't told
anyone in my family.

01:31:26.679 --> 01:31:28.581 position:16% line:89% align:start
Let's keep it our secret.

01:31:31.584 --> 01:31:33.152 position:33% line:89% align:start
How funny...

01:31:33.185 --> 01:31:33.719 position:44% line:89% align:start
What?

01:31:34.855 --> 01:31:38.424 position:19% line:83% align:start
Without Marnie, I would
never have you as my friend.

01:31:38.457 --> 01:31:40.092 position:27% line:89% align:start
That's for sure.

01:31:40.126 --> 01:31:41.394 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

01:31:41.427 --> 01:31:42.562 position:38% line:89% align:start
Marnie...

01:31:42.595 --> 01:31:44.196 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

01:31:46.165 --> 01:31:47.533 position:27% line:89% align:start
The young girl...

01:31:47.568 --> 01:31:50.336 position:30% line:83% align:start
who was trapped
behind the blue window.

01:31:51.738 --> 01:31:53.607 position:10% line:89% align:start
That was quite some time ago.

01:31:54.508 --> 01:31:56.142 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:31:56.577 --> 01:31:57.744 position:47% line:89% align:start
Aw!

01:31:58.445 --> 01:31:59.680 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Sayaka] <i>Exactly.</i>

01:31:59.713 --> 01:32:02.816 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>In order to save her life,</i>
 <i>he makes the decision.</i>

01:32:02.849 --> 01:32:04.083 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>I love that part.</i>

01:32:04.116 --> 01:32:07.588 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Sayaka] <i>Ah, now I want to</i>
 <i>read it all over again.</i>

01:32:07.621 --> 01:32:09.255 position:10% line:89% align:start
Read the sequel next summer?

01:32:09.289 --> 01:32:10.724 position:41% line:83% align:start
- Yeah!
- [Yoriko] <i>Anna!</i>

01:32:14.461 --> 01:32:15.596 position:24% line:89% align:start
Look! It's Auntie!

01:32:16.396 --> 01:32:17.564 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hi!!!

01:32:17.598 --> 01:32:18.732 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Sayaka]
Whoa!

01:32:18.765 --> 01:32:20.233 position:44% line:89% align:start
Anna!

01:32:22.369 --> 01:32:24.504 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Sayaka] <i>Careful! You</i>
 <i>can't just stand up like that!</i>

01:32:24.538 --> 01:32:26.406 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>I got excited.</i>

01:32:26.440 --> 01:32:29.276 position:27% line:89% align:start
[girls laughing]

01:32:32.679 --> 01:32:34.448 position:13% line:89% align:start
Guess what? Auntie's here!

01:32:35.515 --> 01:32:37.884 position:10% line:89% align:start
Ah, Yoriko, good to see you!

01:32:41.321 --> 01:32:43.357 position:33% line:83% align:start
Thank you for
taking care of Anna.

01:32:43.390 --> 01:32:46.928 position:7% line:83% align:start
She's doing well, and she even
made a darling little friend.

01:32:46.961 --> 01:32:48.729 position:16% line:89% align:start
How can I ever repay you?

01:32:48.763 --> 01:32:51.164 position:30% line:83% align:start
Don't be silly.
It was our pleasure.

01:32:51.198 --> 01:32:52.900 position:33% line:83% align:start
We didn't do
anything at all.

01:32:52.934 --> 01:32:54.836 position:27% line:83% align:start
Anna's been great
to have around.

01:32:54.869 --> 01:32:59.272 position:10% line:83% align:start
It was like our daughter had
come home. It was fun.

01:32:59.306 --> 01:33:00.808 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Kiyomasa Oiwa]
I hope she comes again.

01:33:00.842 --> 01:33:02.309 position:41% line:89% align:start
Thanks.

01:33:02.342 --> 01:33:03.543 position:21% line:89% align:start
Let's go talk inside.

01:33:06.413 --> 01:33:09.416 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Setsu] I'm impressed.
You didn't call us once.

01:33:09.449 --> 01:33:10.685 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Yoriko]
Huh?

01:33:10.718 --> 01:33:13.320 position:35% line:89% align:start
[all laugh]

01:33:23.431 --> 01:33:25.165 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'm all packed.

01:33:25.967 --> 01:33:27.167 position:44% line:89% align:start
Anna.

01:33:28.536 --> 01:33:29.537 position:35% line:89% align:start
What is it?

01:33:30.705 --> 01:33:32.440 position:5% line:89% align:start
There's something very important

01:33:32.473 --> 01:33:34.175 position:30% line:83% align:start
that I think we
need to talk about.

01:33:35.476 --> 01:33:38.346 position:30% line:83% align:start
Every month...
we've been receiving subsidies

01:33:38.379 --> 01:33:41.516 position:24% line:83% align:start
from the government
to cover your expenses.

01:33:41.549 --> 01:33:43.284 position:13% line:89% align:start
We didn't want you to know.

01:33:43.317 --> 01:33:46.487 position:21% line:83% align:start
I don't know why but
we just didn't. It just felt...

01:33:46.521 --> 01:33:49.791 position:33% line:83% align:start
- It's fine.
- You must believe me, Anna.

01:33:49.824 --> 01:33:51.826 position:30% line:83% align:start
Whether or not
we receive money,

01:33:51.859 --> 01:33:55.430 position:19% line:83% align:start
nothing can change how
we feel about you.

01:33:55.463 --> 01:33:57.298 position:30% line:89% align:start
I already knew.

01:33:57.331 --> 01:33:59.400 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm happy you told me about
it anyway and I'm really-

01:33:59.434 --> 01:34:00.668 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh Anna!

01:34:00.702 --> 01:34:02.737 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Yoriko cries]

01:34:02.770 --> 01:34:04.205 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Anna sighs]

01:34:06.875 --> 01:34:10.344 position:10% line:83% align:start
I've been looking at all the
photos you'd sent up here.

01:34:10.378 --> 01:34:11.245 position:41% line:89% align:start
Photos?

01:34:11.980 --> 01:34:14.482 position:38% line:83% align:start
Oh, yes.
While you were away,

01:34:14.515 --> 01:34:16.584 position:27% line:83% align:start
I was looking at
old photo albums

01:34:16.618 --> 01:34:18.352 position:16% line:89% align:start
and I found this picture.

01:34:19.353 --> 01:34:20.488 position:27% line:89% align:start
Do you remember?

01:34:20.989 --> 01:34:21.990 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Anna gasps]

01:34:22.825 --> 01:34:24.325 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's the Marsh House!

01:34:24.358 --> 01:34:27.963 position:13% line:83% align:start
When you first came to us,
you wouldn't let it go.

01:34:27.996 --> 01:34:30.331 position:5% line:89% align:start
Someone at the orphanage told me

01:34:30.364 --> 01:34:32.568 position:5% line:89% align:start
it belonged to your grandmother.

01:34:40.409 --> 01:34:42.544 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
My beloved home.

01:34:44.012 --> 01:34:45.380 position:41% line:89% align:start
Marnie!

01:34:47.750 --> 01:34:54.590 position:38% line:89% align:start
[humming]

01:34:54.623 --> 01:35:03.398 position:35% line:89% align:start
[humming]

01:35:03.432 --> 01:35:13.408 position:5% line:83% align:start
- [Marnie] ♪ <i>La la la la la...</i> ♪
- [baby whimpering]

01:35:13.442 --> 01:35:19.615 position:5% line:83% align:start
- [Marnie] ♪ <i>La la la la la...</i> ♪
- [baby whimpering]

01:35:19.648 --> 01:35:24.053 position:21% line:89% align:start
♪ <i>La la la la la...</i> ♪

01:35:24.087 --> 01:35:26.455 position:19% line:89% align:start
That's... who she was.

01:35:26.488 --> 01:35:28.792 position:24% line:89% align:start
[melancholic music]

01:35:28.825 --> 01:35:29.826 position:44% line:89% align:start
Anna?

01:35:34.664 --> 01:35:37.934 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Marnie] <i>And so I was in</i>
 <i>the silo all night long.</i>

01:35:37.967 --> 01:35:41.336 position:5% line:89% align:start
Of course, I was ever so scared.

01:35:41.370 --> 01:35:44.541 position:21% line:83% align:start
But then, that's when
your grandpa came.

01:35:44.574 --> 01:35:48.444 position:27% line:83% align:start
He encouraged me,
saying I did well.

01:35:48.478 --> 01:35:51.948 position:24% line:83% align:start
I've overcome many
frightening things in life.

01:35:51.981 --> 01:35:53.850 position:19% line:89% align:start
And Anna, so will you.

01:35:54.984 --> 01:35:55.952 position:35% line:89% align:start
After all,

01:35:55.985 --> 01:35:57.854 position:13% line:89% align:start
you're my only grandchild.

01:35:57.887 --> 01:36:01.591 position:21% line:83% align:start
And you have my love,
now and forever.

01:36:03.726 --> 01:36:04.994 position:35% line:89% align:start
Forever...

01:36:08.665 --> 01:36:12.802 position:27% line:89% align:start
[peaceful music]

01:36:41.065 --> 01:36:45.870 position:30% line:89% align:start
[bright music]

01:36:49.139 --> 01:36:50.174 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

01:36:50.207 --> 01:36:51.407 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
 <i>Excuse me?</i>

01:36:53.043 --> 01:36:54.044 position:44% line:89% align:start
Anna?

01:36:55.646 --> 01:36:57.648 position:7% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry about the other day.

01:36:59.917 --> 01:37:02.385 position:13% line:83% align:start
Next year, you better join
us for trash pickup.

01:37:09.927 --> 01:37:11.428 position:24% line:89% align:start
Was that a friend?

01:37:11.462 --> 01:37:12.463 position:35% line:89% align:start
Uh, maybe.

01:37:18.936 --> 01:37:20.537 position:35% line:89% align:start
Hi Hisako!

01:37:24.074 --> 01:37:24.608 position:33% line:89% align:start
Anna. Hello.

01:37:25.809 --> 01:37:28.679 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm... I'm going
home to Sapporo now.

01:37:28.712 --> 01:37:30.514 position:30% line:89% align:start
Is that right?

01:37:30.547 --> 01:37:31.982 position:30% line:83% align:start
Judging by the
look on your face,

01:37:32.016 --> 01:37:34.652 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'd say something
good has happened.

01:37:34.685 --> 01:37:37.755 position:16% line:83% align:start
Yes, lots of good things.
I'm really happy now.

01:37:37.788 --> 01:37:38.789 position:44% line:89% align:start
Good.

01:37:39.823 --> 01:37:42.127 position:30% line:83% align:start
And this is...
this is my mother.

01:37:43.261 --> 01:37:44.963 position:10% line:89% align:start
Thank... thank you very much

01:37:44.996 --> 01:37:47.098 position:33% line:83% align:start
for all your
kindness with Anna.

01:37:47.132 --> 01:37:49.767 position:13% line:89% align:start
Truly, it was my pleasure.

01:37:49.800 --> 01:37:51.535 position:24% line:83% align:start
Let's draw together
again next summer,

01:37:51.568 --> 01:37:53.071 position:27% line:83% align:start
- shall we, Anna?
- Yes!

01:37:53.104 --> 01:37:54.505 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'll write you a letter.

01:37:54.538 --> 01:37:56.540 position:21% line:83% align:start
I have some wonderful
news to tell you.

01:37:56.573 --> 01:37:57.574 position:35% line:89% align:start
Thank you!

01:37:59.710 --> 01:38:01.846 position:33% line:83% align:start
Again, thank
you very much.

01:38:07.786 --> 01:38:09.220 position:30% line:89% align:start
Wonderful news?

01:38:09.254 --> 01:38:11.656 position:44% line:83% align:start
Yeah,
I'll tell you about it later.

01:38:11.690 --> 01:38:12.590 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Yoriko]
Oh, why not now?

01:38:13.692 --> 01:38:15.894 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Anna]
I promise I'll tell you later.

01:38:26.004 --> 01:38:30.709 position:16% line:89% align:start
Toichi! Sayaka! Goodbye!

01:38:31.843 --> 01:38:34.212 position:30% line:89% align:start
[bright music]

